Pool }}</em></strong>'=>'Ugyldigt <strong>{{ fieldName }}</strong> navn. Brug kun <strong><em>{{ characterPool }}</em></strong>','Backend / Validation / Alert MessageThe value in the <strong>{{ fieldName }}</strong> field is not a valid hex color code.'=>'Værdien i feltet <strong>{{ fieldName }}</strong> er ikke en gyldig hexfarvekode.','Backend / Global / Validation MessageThe <strong>{{ fieldName }}</strong> has to be an integer bigger than {{ limit }}.'=>'<strong>{{ fieldName }}</strong> skal være et heltal, der er større end {{ limit }}.','Backend / Validation / Alert MessagePlease fill out the field <strong>{{ fieldName }}</strong>. The field must have at least {{ minLength }} characters and contains only characters from <strong><em>{{ characterPool }}</em></strong>.'=>'Udfyld feltet <strong>{{ fieldName }}</strong>. Feltet skal have mindst {{ minLength }} tegn og må kun indeholde tegn fra <strong><em>{{ characterPool }}</em></strong>.','Backend / Validation / Alert MessagePlease fill out the field <strong>{{ fieldName }}</strong>.'=>'Udfyld feltet <strong>{{ fieldName }}</strong>.','Backend / Validation / Alert MessagePlease change the name of the <strong>{{ fieldName }}</strong>. Your selected name for <strong>{{ fieldName }}</strong> is reserved and can not be used.'=>'Ændr navnet på <strong>{{ fieldName }}</strong>. Dit valgte navn for <strong>{{ fieldName</strong> er reserveret og kan ikke bruges.','Backend / Validation / Alert MessageThe <strong>{{ fieldName }}</strong> already exists.'=>'<strong>{{ fieldName }}</strong> findes allerede.','Backend / Validation / Alert MessageThe value in the <strong>{{ fieldName }}</strong> field is not a valid url.'=>'Værdien i feltet <strong>{{ fieldName }}</strong> er ikke en gyldig URL.','Backend / Content Blocker Language String / Alert MessageThe <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Status">IAB TCF Status</translation-key> option is currently active, located under <em><translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Consent Management</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Iab-Tcf">IAB TCF</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Iab-Tcf-Settings">Settings</translation-key></em>. Therefore, modifications to this setting are not permitted.'=>'Indstillingen <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Status">IAB TCF-status</translation-key> er i øjeblikket aktiv og findes under <em><translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Samtykkehåndtering</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Iab-Tcf">IAB TCF</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Iab-Tcf-Settings">Indstillinger</translation-key></em>. Derfor er det ikke tilladt at ændre denne indstilling.','Backend / Widget / BreadcrumbWidget'=>'Widget','Backend / Widget / LabelColor'=>'Farve','Backend / Widget / LabelPosition'=>'Position','Backend / Widget / Label<translation-key id="Show-Widget">Show Widget</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Show-Widget">Vis widget</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcodes</translation-key> are not available until the <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> is created.'=>'<translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcodesene</translation-key> er ikke tilgængelige, før <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppen</translation-key> er oprettet.','Backend / Cookie Box / HeadlineReset Widget Settings'=>'Nulstil widgetindstillinger','Backend / Service Groups / Alert MessageCould not delete <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> because <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> is linked with <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key>.'=>'Kunne ikke slette <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppen</translation-key>, fordi <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppe</translation-key> er knyttet til <translation-key id="Services">Servicer</translation-key>.','Backend / Widget / HeadlineWidget Settings'=>'Widgetindstillinger','Backend / Service Group / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> configured.'=>'Der er ikke konfigureret nogen <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppe</translation-key>.','Backend / Widget / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset all <translation-key id="Widget">Widget</translation-key> settings. They will be reset to their default settings.'=>'Bekræft, at du vil nulstille alle indstillinger for <translation-key id="Widget">Widget</translation-key>. De vil blive nulstillet til deres standardindstillinger.','Backend / Service Groups / HeadlineReset Default Service Groups'=>'Nulstil standardservicegrupper','Backend / Widget / Select OptionBottom Left'=>'Nederst venstre','Backend / Service Groups / HeadlineService Groups'=>'Servicegrupper','Backend / Widget / Select OptionBottom Right'=>'Nederst højre','Backend / Service Groups / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset the <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Service Groups</translation-key>. They will be reset to their default settings. Your custom <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Service Groups</translation-key> remain unchanged.'=>'Bekræft, at du ønsker at nulstille <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Servicegrupperne</translation-key>. De vil blive nulstillet til deres standardindstillinger. Dine tilpassede <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Servicegrupper</translation-key> forbliver uændrede.','Backend / Service Groups / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Init / Plugin LinksDashboard'=>'Kontrolpanel','Backend / Service Groups / Table HeadlineName'=>'Navn','Backend / Init / Plugin LinksLicense'=>'Licens','Backend / Service Groups / Table HeadlinePosition'=>'Position','Backend / Service Groups / Table HeadlineStatus'=>'Status','Backend / Settings / FieldsBar'=>'Bar','Backend / Service Groups / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Service Groups</translation-key> section?'=>'Hvad er formålet med sektionen <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Servicegrupper</translation-key>?','Backend / Settings / FieldsFoo'=>'Foo','Backend / Service Groups / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Symboler forklaret','Backend / Service Groups / Things to know / Text<translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> can be grouped thematically into <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Service Groups</translation-key> which are displayed to the visitor. Unused <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Service Groups</translation-key> can be disabled, new ones can be added. The <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Essential">Essential</translation-key> cannot be deactivated. All <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> belonging to <translation-key id="Essential">Essential</translation-key> are always issued. An active <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> is only displayed in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>, if at least one active <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is assigned to it.'=>'<translation-key id="Services">Servicer</translation-key> kan grupperes tematisk i <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Servicegrupper</translation-key>, som vises for den besøgende. Ubrugte <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Servicegrupper</translation-key> kan deaktiveres, og nye kan tilføjes. <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppen</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Essential">Nødvendige</translation-key> kan ikke deaktiveres. Alle <translation-key id="Services">Servicer</translation-key>, der hører til <translation-key id="Essential">Nødvendige</translation-key>, udstedes altid. En aktiv <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppe</translation-key> vises kun i <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key>, hvis den er tildelt mindst én aktiv <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Groups / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> is active and displayed in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>. Not available for the <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Essential">Essential</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppen</translation-key> er aktiv og vises i <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key>. Ikke tilgængelig for <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppen</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Essential">Nødvendige</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Groups / Things to know / TextDelete the <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>. Not available for default <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Service Groups</translation-key>.'=>'Slet <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppen</translation-key>. Ikke tilgængelig for <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Servicegrupper</translation-key>, der er standard.','Backend / Service Groups / Things to know / TextEdit the <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>.'=>'Redigér <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppen</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Groups / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> is inactive and not displayed in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>. Not available for the <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Essential">Essential</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppen</translation-key> er inaktiv og vises ikke i <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key>. Ikke tilgængelig for <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppen</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Essential">Nødvendige</translation-key>.','Backend / Settings / Alert MessageYour configured domain is different from the website domain. The setting may be incorrect and will cause the Dialog to reappear on each page.'=>'Dit konfigurerede domæne er forskelligt fra hjemmesidens domæne. Indstillingen kan være forkert og vil få Dialogboksen til at dukke op igen på hver side.','Backend / Settings / Alert MessageYou have enabled <translation-key id="Do-Not-Track">&quot;Do Not Track&quot;</translation-key> in your browser therefore you will not see the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> on your website.'=>'Du har aktiveret <translation-key id="Do-Not-Track">&quot;Do Not Track&quot;</translation-key> i din browser, og derfor vil du ikke se <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key> på din hjemmeside.','Backend / Settings / Alert MessageIf this option is active, most likely all visits will be counted as "Direct visits" and the origin will be lost. We therefore recommend not to activate this option!'=>'Hvis denne indstilling er aktiv, vil alle besøg sandsynligvis blive optalt som "Direkte besøg", og oprindelsen vil gå tabt. Vi anbefaler derfor ikke at aktivere denne mulighed!','Backend / Settings / Alert MessageOnly activate this option if you need to reload your page after consent. Less than 1 &#37; of all <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> customers need this option enabled. If you don\'t know if you need this option, you won\'t need it.'=>'Aktivér kun denne mulighed, hvis du har brug for at genindlæse din side efter samtykke. Mindre end 1 % af alle <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>-kunder har brug for at aktivere denne mulighed. Hvis du ikke ved, om du har brug for denne mulighed, så har du ikke brug for den.','Backend / Settings / BreadcrumbGeneral Settings'=>'Generelle indstillinger','Backend / Settings / LabelAggregate Consents'=>'Aggregér samtykker','Backend / Settings / LabelAutomatic Domain and Path Detection'=>'Automatisk registrering af domæne og sti','Backend / Settings / Label<translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie-Status">Borlabs Cookie Status</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie-Status">Borlabs Cookie-status</translation-key>','Backend / Settings / LabelDomain'=>'Domæne','Backend / Settings / LabelCookie Lifetime in Days'=>'Cookielevetid i dage','Backend / Settings / LabelCookie Lifetime in Days - Essential Only'=>'Cookielevetid i dage - Kun Nødvendige','Backend / Settings / LabelPath'=>'Sti','Backend / Settings / Label<translation-key id="Secure-Attribute">Secure attribute</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Secure-Attribute">Secure-attribut</translation-key>','Backend / Settings / LabelCookie Version'=>'Cookieversion','Backend / Settings / LabelCookies for Bots/Crawlers'=>'Cookies til bots/crawlere','Backend / Settings / LabelCross Cookie Domains'=>'Cross-cookie-domæner - Domæner','Backend / Plugin Settings / LabelDisplay Meta Box'=>'Vis metaboks','Backend / Settings / LabelReload After Opt-in'=>'Genindlæs efter opt-in','Backend / Settings / LabelReload After Opt-out'=>'Genindlæs efter opt-out','Backend / Settings / LabelSetup Mode'=>'Opsætning','Backend / Settings / Label<translation-key id="UpdateCookieVersionForceRe-Selection">Update Cookie Version &amp; Force Re-Selection</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="UpdateCookieVersionForceRe-Selection">Opdatér cookieversion og tving genvalg</translation-key>','Backend / Settings / HeadlineCookie Settings'=>'Cookieindstillinger','Backend / Settings / HeadlineGeneral Settings'=>'Generelle indstillinger','Backend / Settings / HeadlineReset General Settings'=>'Nulstil generelle indstillinger','Backend / Settings / HintAggregate the consents of all WordPress sites in one table.'=>'Sammentæl samtykkerne fra alle WordPress-hjemmesider i én tabel.','Backend / Settings / Hint<translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> tries to automatically detect domain and path.'=>'<translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> forsøger automatisk at registrere domæne og sti.','Backend / Settings / HintActivates <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> on your website. Displays the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> and blocks iframes and other external media.'=>'Aktiverer <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> på din hjemmeside. Viser <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key> og blokerer iframes og andre eksterne medier.','Backend / Settings / HintSpecify the domain scheme for which the cookie is valid. Example: If you enter <strong><em>example.com</em></strong> the cookie is also valid for subdomains like <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>.'=>'Angiv det domæne, som cookien er gyldig for. For eksempel: Hvis du indtaster <strong><em>example.com</em></strong> er cookien også gyldig for underdomæner som <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>.','Backend / Settings / HintNumber of days until the visitor is asked again for their consent. Remember to adjust the <translation-key id="Cookie-Lifetime">Cookie Lifetime</translation-key> information of the <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> <translation-key id="Cookie">Cookie</translation-key> under <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.'=>'Antal dage indtil den besøgende bliver bedt om at give sit samtykke igen. Husk at justere oplysningerne om <translation-key id="Cookie-Lifetime">Cookielevetid</translation-key> for <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> <translation-key id="Cookie">Cookie</translation-key> under <translation-key id="Services">Servicer</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.','Backend / Settings / HintThe path for which the cookie is valid. Default path: <strong>{{ networkPath }}</strong>'=>'Stien som cookien er gyldig til. Standardsti: <strong>{{ networkPath }}</strong>','Backend / Settings / HintThe <translation-key id="SameSite-Attribute">SameSite attribute</translation-key> defines how the browser should handle cookies in cross-site requests. We recommend using the <strong>Lax</strong> option.'=>'<translation-key id="SameSite-Attribute">SameSite-attribut</translation-key>ten definerer, hvordan browseren skal håndtere cookies i cross-site-anmodninger. Vi anbefaler at bruge indstillingen <strong>Lax</strong>.','Backend / Settings / HintA cookie with the <translation-key id="Secure-Attribute">Secure attribute</translation-key> is sent to the server only in case of an encrypted request via the HTTPS protocol.'=>'En cookie med <translation-key id="Secure-Attribute">Secure-attribut</translation-key>ten sendes kun til serveren i tilfælde af en krypteret anmodning via HTTPS-protokollen.','Backend / Settings / HintShows the version of the cookie of <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. Increases with activating <translation-key id="UpdateCookieVersionForceRe-Selection">Update Cookie Version &amp; Force Re-Selection</translation-key>.'=>'Viser versionen af <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. Øges med aktivering af <translation-key id="UpdateCookieVersionForceRe-Selection">Opdatér cookieversion og tving genvalg</translation-key>.','Backend / Settings / HintA bot/crawler is treated like a visitor who accepted all <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key>.'=>'En bot/crawler behandles som en besøgende, der har accepteret alle <translation-key id="Services">Servicer</translation-key>.','Backend / Settings / HintAdd one URL per line. Insert WordPress Address (URL). URL must end with <strong>/</strong>. Consent will be shared between websites.'=>'Tilføj en URL pr. linje. Indsæt WordPress-adresse (URL). URL\'en skal slutte med <strong>/</strong> Samtykke vil blive delt mellem hjemmesider.','Backend / Settings / HintDisplay the <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Meta Box</translation-key> on the selected post types. The <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Meta Box</translation-key> allows you to add custom JavaScript on specific pages.'=>'Vis <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Metaboks</translation-key> på de valgte indlægstyper. <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Metaboksen</translation-key> giver dig mulighed for at tilføje tilpasset JavaScript på bestemte sider.','Backend / Settings / HintIf enabled, the website will be reloaded after the visitor saves their consent.'=>'Hvis aktiveret vil hjemmesiden blive genindlæst, når den besøgende har gemt sit samtykke.','Backend / Settings / HintIf enabled, the website will be reloaded after the visitor opt out.'=>'Hvis aktiveret vil hjemmesiden blive genindlæst, når den besøgende har valgt opt-out.','Backend / Dialog Appearance / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset all <translation-key id="Settings">Settings</translation-key> settings. They will be reset to their default settings.'=>'Bekræft, at du ønsker at nulstille alle <translation-key id="Settings">Indstillinger</translation-key>. De vil blive nulstillet til deres standardindstillinger.','Backend / Settings / HintA visitor with active <translation-key id="Do-Not-Track">&quot;Do Not Track&quot;</translation-key> setting will not see the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> automatically selects the <translation-key id="Accept-Only-Essential">Accept Only Essential</translation-key> option.'=>'En besøgende med aktiv <translation-key id="Do-Not-Track">&quot;Do Not Track&quot;</translation-key>-indstilling vil ikke se <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key>, og <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> vælger automatisk indstillingen <translation-key id="Accept-Only-Essential">Acceptér kun nødvendige</translation-key>.','Backend / Settings / HintWith Setup Mode enabled, you can test your setup without having to enable <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie-Status">Borlabs Cookie Status</translation-key>. Only you will see the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> on your website.'=>'Når opsætningstilstand er aktiveret, kan du teste din opsætning uden at skulle aktivere <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie-Status">Borlabs Cookie-status</translation-key>. Kun du vil se <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key> på din hjemmeside.','Backend / Settings / HintUpdates the version of the cookie of <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. This will cause the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> to reappear for visitors who have already selected an option.'=>'Opdaterer cookieversionen for <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. Dette får <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key> til at dukke op igen for besøgende, der allerede har valgt en mulighed.','Backend / Settings / TextVersion'=>'Version','Backend / Settings / Things to know / TextWhen you have to aggregate the consent:'=>'Når du skal sammentælle samtykket:','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Text- if one site is using only the domain (e.g. <strong><em>example.com</em></strong>) and the other site a subdomain (e.g. <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>)'=>'- Hvis en hjemmeside kun bruger domænet (f.eks. <strong><em>example.com</em></strong>) og den anden side et underdomæne (f.eks. <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>)','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Text- if one site is using the root folder <strong>/</strong> and the other site a subfolder (e.g. <strong>/shop</strong>)'=>'- hvis den ene side bruger rodmappen <strong>/</strong> og den anden side en undermappe (f.eks. <strong>/shop</strong>)','Backend / Settings / Things to know / TextWhen you can separate the consent:'=>'Når du kan adskille samtykket:','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Text- if all sites are using different domains (e.g. <strong><em>example.com</em></strong> and <strong><em>my-example.com</em></strong>) or different subdomains (e.g. <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong> and <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>)'=>'- hvis alle sider bruger forskellige domæner (f.eks. <strong><em>example.com</em></strong> og <strong><em>my-example.com</em></strong>) eller forskellige underdomæner (f.eks. <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong> og <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>)','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Text- if all sites are using different subfolders (e.g. <strong>/en</strong> and <strong>/de</strong>)'=>'- hvis alle sider bruger forskellige undermapper (f.eks. <strong>/en</strong> og <strong>/de</strong>)','Backend / Settings / Things to know / TextThe visitor\'s consent is transferred to all specified domains and WordPress installations, provided the websites are set up in the same way (<translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> IDs must match). Any consent or modification by the visitor will be shared with the specified domains.'=>'Den besøgendes samtykke overføres til alle specificerede domæner og WordPress-installationer, forudsat at hjemmesiderne er sat op på samme måde (<translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> og <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppe</translation-key>-id\'er skal matche). Ethvert samtykke eller ændring fra den besøgende vil blive delt med de angivne domæner.','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Text<a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="%s" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span>More information about <translation-key id="Cross-Cookie-Domains">Cross Cookie Domains</translation-key></span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>'=>'<a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="%s" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span>Flere oplysninger om <translation-key id="Cross-Cookie-Domains">Cross-cookie-domæner - Domæner</translation-key></span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>','Backend / Settings / Things to know / HeadlineAggregate Consents'=>'Aggregér samtykker','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Cross-Cookie-Domains">Cross Cookie Domains</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Cross-Cookie-Domains">Cross-cookie-domæner - Domæner</translation-key>','Backend / Settings / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the Cookie Version?'=>'Hvilken cookieversion er det?','Backend / Plugin Settings / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the Meta Box?'=>'Hvad er Metaboksen?','Backend / Settings / Things to know / TextThe cookie of <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> is assigned a version number. It is used to ask the visitor again for their consent if changes have been made to the <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key>. If the version number in the cookie differs from the current version number, the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> appears to the visitor.'=>'Cookien fra <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> er tildelt et versionsnummer. Det bruges til at bede den besøgende om samtykke igen, hvis der er foretaget ændringer i <translation-key id="Services">Servicerne</translation-key>. Hvis versionsnummeret i cookien adskiller sig fra det aktuelle versionsnummer, vises <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key> for den besøgende.','Backend / Plugin Settings / Things to know / TextIf active the <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Meta Box</translation-key> is displayed in the selected post types. This allows you to execute code (JavaScript, HTML, <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcodes</translation-key>) on the page and e.g. trigger a conversion pixel.'=>'Hvis den er aktiv, vises <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Metaboksen</translation-key> i de valgte indlægstyper. Dette giver dig mulighed for at udføre kode (JavaScript, HTML, <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcodes</translation-key>) på siden og f.eks. udløse en konverteringspixel.','Backend / Style Blocker / BreadcrumbEdit: {{ name }}'=>'Redigér: {{ name }}','Backend / Style Blocker / BreadcrumbStyle Blockers'=>'Stilblokkere','Backend / Style Blocker / BreadcrumbNew'=>'Ny','Backend / Script Blocker / Field LabelContent Blocker Global JavaScript'=>'Indholdsblokker global JavaScript','Backend / Style Blocker / LabelHandles'=>'Handles','Backend / Style Blocker / LabelID'=>'ID','Backend / Style Blocker / LabelName'=>'Navn','Backend / Style Blocker / LabelPhrases'=>'Udtryk','Backend / Script Blocker / LabelService Opt-in Script Tag'=>'Service opt-in script tag','Backend / Style Blocker / LabelStatus'=>'Status','Backend / Style Blocker / HeadlineStyle Blocker Configuration'=>'Konfiguration af stilblokkere','Backend / Style Blocker / HeadlineStyle Blocker Information'=>'Oplysninger om stilblokkere','Backend / Style Blocker / HeadlineStyle Blocker Settings'=>'Indstillinger for stilblokkere','Backend / Script Blocker / HintIf your intention is to unblock previously blocked <translation-key id="Styles">Styles</translation-key> upon unblocking a <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>, please insert the provided JavaScript into the <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> field within your <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> settings.'=>'Hvis din hensigt er at fjerne blokeringen af tidligere blokerede <translation-key id="Styles">Stile</translation-key>, når du fjerner blokeringen af en <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokker</translation-key>, skal du indsætte det medfølgende JavaScript i feltet <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> i indstillingerne for din <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokker</translation-key>.','Backend / Style Blocker / Hint<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be set. The <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be at least 3 characters long and may only contain: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>'=>'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> skal være indstillet. <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key>\'et skal være mindst tre tegn langt og må kun indeholde: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>','Backend / Style Blocker / HintThe name of the <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'Navnet på <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Stilblokkeren</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blocker / HintTo allow the unblocking of previously blocked <translation-key id="Styles">Styles</translation-key> through user consent for a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>, please insert the ensuing script tag into the field labeled <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> within your <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'For at tillade at blokeringen fjernes af tidligere blokerede <translation-key id="Styles">Stile</translation-key> gennem brugersamtykke til en <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>, skal du indsætte det følgende script tag i feltet mærket <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in-kode</translation-key> i din <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Style Blocker / HintThe status of this <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key>. If the <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> is disabled, it will not block stylesheets and style-tags.'=>'Status for denne <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Stilblokker</translation-key>. Hvis <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Stilblokkeren</translation-key> er deaktiveret, vil den ikke blokere stylesheets og style tags.','Backend / Style Blockers / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> configured.'=>'Ingen <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Stilblokker</translation-key> konfigureret.','Backend / Style Blockers / BreadcrumbStyle Blockers'=>'Stilblokkere','Backend / Style Blockers / HeadlineStyle Blockers'=>'Stilblokkere','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlineHandles'=>'Handles','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlineName'=>'Navn','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlinePhrases'=>'Udtryk','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlineStatus'=>'Status','Backend / Style Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key> section?'=>'Hvad er formålet med sektionen <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Stilblokkere</translation-key>?','Backend / Style Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Symboler forklaret','Backend / Style Blockers / Tip / HeadlineLanguage independent'=>'Uafhængig af sprog','Backend / Style Blockers / Tip / Text<translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key> are configured independently for all languages.'=>'<translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Stilblokkere</translation-key> konfigureres uafhængigt af hinanden for alle sprog.','Backend / Style Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key> section allows you to block <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> from <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> that, for example, embed <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> to load external fonts like <translation-key id="Google-Fonts">Google Fonts</translation-key>.'=>'I sektionen <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Stilblokkere</translation-key> kan du blokere <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> fra <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key>, der f.eks. indlejrer <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> for at indlæse eksterne skrifttyper som <translation-key id="Google-Fonts">Google Fonts</translation-key>.','Backend / Style Blockers / Things to know / TextOnce a <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> is created, <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> provides an unblock JavaScript that can be entered into the <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> field of a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. The <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> becomes unblocked once a visitor consents to the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Når en <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Stilblokker</translation-key> er oprettet, leverer <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> et JavaScript, der fjerner blokeringen, og som kan indtastes i feltet <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in-kode</translation-key> i en <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. Blokeringen af <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key>\'en bliver fjernet, når en besøgende samtykker til <translation-key id="Service">Servicen</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> is enabled and actively prevents <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> execution if the <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Phrases">Phrases</translation-key> matches a term configured in the system.'=>'<translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Stilblokkeren</translation-key> er aktiveret og forhindrer aktiv udførelse af <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key>, hvis <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> eller <translation-key id="Phrases">Udtryk</translation-key> matcher et udtryk, der er konfigureret i systemet.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextDelete the <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key>. Not available for a <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> installed via the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key>.'=>'Slet <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Stilblokkeren</translation-key>. Ikke tilgængelig for en <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Stilblokker</translation-key>, der er installeret via <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Biblioteket</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextEdit the <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'Redigér <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Stilblokkeren</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> is inactive, allowing all <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> are executed without filtering or restricting based on <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Phrases">Phrases</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Stilblokkeren</translation-key> er inaktiv, så al <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> kan udføres uden filtrering eller begrænsning baseret på <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> eller <translation-key id="Phrases">Udtryk</translation-key>.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessageConnecting to the API failed. Please check that WordPress has access to the Internet or retry later.'=>'Forbindelsen til API\'en mislykkedes. Tjek, at WordPress har adgang til internettet, eller prøv igen senere.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessageMoving the database file failed.'=>'Flytning af databasefilen mislykkedes.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessagePlease enable GeoIP before downloading the database.'=>'Aktivér GeoIP, før du downloader databasen.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessageThe database was successfully updated.'=>'Databasen blev succesfuldt opdateret.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessageYou already have the most up-to-date database.'=>'Du har allerede den mest opdaterede database.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessageUnpacking the database to the temporary folder failed. Please check if the temporary folder is writable and the PHP module ZIP is installed.'=>'Udpakning af databasen til den midlertidige mappe mislykkedes. Tjek venligst, om den midlertidige mappe er skrivbar, og om PHP-modulet ZIP er installeret.','Backend / Model Localization / ModelCompatibility Patch'=>'Kompatibilitetsrettelse','Backend / Model Localization / ModelContent Blocker'=>'Indholdsblokker','Backend / Model Localization / ModelProvider'=>'Udbyder','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Tracking">Tracking</translation-key> cookies are used to analyze user behavior on the website and to optimize the website based on the results.'=>'Cookies til <translation-key id="Tracking">Sporing</translation-key> bruges til at analysere brugernes adfærd på hjemmesiden og til at optimere hjemmesiden på baggrund af resultaterne.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Type">Type</translation-key>: Choose where information is stored in the browser. <translation-key id="HTTP">HTTP</translation-key> cookies are commonly used, alternatives like <translation-key id="Local-Storage">Local Storage</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Session-Storage">Session Storage</translation-key> do not possess predetermined lifetimes.'=>'<translation-key id="Type">Type</translation-key>: Vælg, hvor oplysningerne skal gemmes i browseren. <translation-key id="HTTP">HTTP</translation-key>-cookies er almindeligt anvendt, alternativer som <translation-key id="Local-Storage">Lokal opbevaring</translation-key> eller <translation-key id="Session-Storage">Sessionsopbevaring</translation-key> har ikke forudbestemte levetider.','Backend / Services / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> selected.'=>'Der er ikke valgt nogen <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppe</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / AlertThe selected <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> is not available in the current language.'=>'Den valgte <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyder</translation-key> er ikke tilgængelig på det aktuelle sprog.','Backend / Services / Alert MessageThe selected <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> does not exist.'=>'Den valgte <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyder</translation-key> findes ikke.','Backend / Services / Alert MessageThe selected <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> does not exist.'=>'Den valgte <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppe</translation-key> findes ikke.','Backend / Services / Alert MessageThe selected <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> is not available in the current language.'=>'Den valgte <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppe</translation-key> er ikke tilgængelig på det aktuelle sprog.','Backend / Services / Alert MessageThe selected <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is not available in the current language.'=>'Den valgte <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> er ikke tilgængelig på det aktuelle sprog.','Backend / Service / BreadcrumbEdit: {{ name }}'=>'Redigér: {{ name }}','Backend / Services / BreadcrumbServices'=>'Servicer','Backend / Services / BreadcrumbNew'=>'Ny','Backend / Services / LabelDescription'=>'Beskrivelse','Backend / Services / LabelFallback Code'=>'Fallback-kode','Backend / Services / LabelID'=>'ID','Backend / Services / LabelName'=>'Navn','Backend / Services / Label<translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in-kode</translation-key>','Backend / Services / LabelOpt-out Code'=>'Opt-out-kode','Backend / Services / Label<translation-key id="Opt-out-Shortcode">Opt-out Shortcode</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Opt-out-Shortcode">Opt-out-shortcode</translation-key>','Backend / Services / LabelPosition'=>'Position','Backend / Services / LabelProvider List'=>'Liste over udbydere','Backend / Services / LabelService Group'=>'Servicegruppe','Backend / Services / Label<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key>','Backend / Services / LabelStatus'=>'Status','Backend / Services / HeadlineHTML &amp; JavaScript'=>'HTML og JavaScript','Backend / Services / HeadlineProvider Information'=>'Udbyderoplysninger','Backend / Services / HeadlineService Group Information'=>'Servicegruppeoplysninger','Backend / Services / HeadlineService Information'=>'Serviceoplysninger','Backend / Services / HeadlineService Settings'=>'Servicindstillinger','Backend / Services / HintExplain to your visitors what this <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> does.'=>'Forklar dine besøgende, hvad denne <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> gør.','Backend / Services / HintThis code will always be executed.'=>'Denne kode vil altid blive udført.','Backend / Services / Hint<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be set. The <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be at least 3 characters long and may only contain: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>'=>'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> skal være indstillet. <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key>\'et skal være mindst tre tegn langt og må kun indeholde: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>','Backend / Services / HintInsert a name for this <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Indsæt et navn for denne <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / HintThis code is executed after the visitor has given their consent.'=>'Denne kode udføres, når den besøgende har givet sit samtykke.','Backend / Services / HintThis code is executed only if the visitor has previously consented and now chooses to opt out. It is executed once.'=>'Denne kode udføres kun, hvis den besøgende tidligere har samtykket og nu vælger at melde sig ud. Den udføres én gang.','Backend / Services / HintUse this <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> to display an opt-out option for this <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Brug denne <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> til at vise en mulighed for opt-out for denne <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / HintDetermine the position where this <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is displayed in its <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>. Order follows natural numbers.'=>'Bestem den position, hvor denne <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> vises i sin <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppe</translation-key>. Rækkefølgen følger naturlige tal.','Backend / Services / HintA <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> must be linked to a <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>. You may choose an existing <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> or establish a new one. Please note, the option to create a new <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> is available exclusively during the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> creation process within this view.'=>'En <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> skal være knyttet til en <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyder</translation-key>. Du kan vælge en eksisterende <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyder</translation-key> eller oprette en ny. Bemærk, at muligheden for at oprette en ny <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyder</translation-key> udelukkende er tilgængelig under oprettelsesprocessen for <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>r i denne visning.','Backend / Services / HintThe <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is part of.'=>'<translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppe</translation-key> som <translation-key id="Service">Servicen</translation-key> er en del af.','Backend / Services / HintUse this <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> to unblock JavaScript or content when user opted-in for this <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Brug denne <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> til at fjerne blokeringen af JavaScript eller indhold, når brugeren har valgt denne <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / HintThe status of this <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. If enabled it is displayed to the visitor in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'Status for denne <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. Hvis den er aktiveret, vises den for den besøgende i <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / Input Placeholder...block this...'=>'... blokér dette ...','Backend / Services / Input PlaceholderNever'=>'Aldrig','Backend / Services / Table HeadlineLifetime'=>'Levetid','Backend / Services / Table HeadlineName'=>'Navn','Backend / Library / HintThe <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> are included in this package and are necessary for the proper functioning of this package. They are installed when you click the <translation-key id="Button-Install">Install</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Reinstall">Reinstall</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Update">Update</translation-key> button. You can locate them later using the displayed name and key in the <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> view (<translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Consent Management</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Services">Services</translation-key>).'=>'<translation-key id="Services">Servicerne</translation-key> er inkluderet i denne pakke og er nødvendige for, at denne pakke fungerer korrekt. De installeres, når du klikker på knappen <translation-key id="Button-Install">Installér</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Reinstall">Geninstallér</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Update">Opdatér</translation-key>. Du kan finde dem senere ved hjælp af det viste navn og nøglen i visningen <translation-key id="Services">Servicer</translation-key> vis (<translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Samtykkehåndtering</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Services">Servicer</translation-key>).','Backend / Services / Table HeadlinePurpose'=>'Formål','Backend / Library / HintThe <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key> are included in this package and are necessary for the proper functioning of this package. They are installed when you click the <translation-key id="Button-Install">Install</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Reinstall">Reinstall</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Update">Update</translation-key> button. You can locate them later using the displayed name and key in the <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key> view (<translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers">Blockers</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key>).'=>'<translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Stilblokkerne</translation-key> er inkluderet i denne pakke og er nødvendige for, at denne pakke fungerer korrekt. De installeres, når du klikker på knappen <translation-key id="Button-Install">Installér</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Reinstall">Geninstallér</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Update">Opdatér</translation-key>. Du kan finde dem senere ved hjælp af det viste navn og nøglen i visningen <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Stilblokkere</translation-key> vis (<translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers">Blokkere</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Style-Blockers">Stilblokkere</translation-key>).','Backend / Services / Table HeadlineType'=>'Type','Backend / Library / NavigationAll'=>'Alle','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextIf you enable this option <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> searches and deletes cookies that match the <translation-key id="Name">Name</translation-key> (<translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Name">Name</translation-key>). You can also use <strong>*</strong> to search for multiple names, e.g. if you enter the Name <strong><em>example_*</em></strong> <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> will search and delete the cookies <strong><em>example_abc</em></strong> and <strong><em>example_xyz</em></strong>.'=>'Hvis du aktiverer denne mulighed, søger <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> efter og sletter cookies, der matcher <translation-key id="Name">Navn</translation-key> (<translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Name">Navn</translation-key>). Du kan også bruge <strong>*</strong> til at søge efter flere navne, f.eks. hvis du indtaster Navnet <strong><em>example_*</em></strong> vil <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> søge efter og slette cookies <strong><em>example_abc</em></strong> og <strong><em>example_xyz</em></strong>.','Backend / Library / NavigationFilter'=>'Filter','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThis function is mainly intended to delete session cookies set by third-party plugins via PHP. JavaScript cookies can also be deleted, but only if they belong to the same domain and do not have the <translation-key id="Secure-Attribute">Secure attribute</translation-key>.'=>'Denne funktion er primært beregnet til at slette sessionscookies, der er indstillet af tredjepartsplugins via PHP. JavaScript-cookies kan også slettes, men kun hvis de tilhører det samme domæne og ikke har <translation-key id="Secure-Attribute">Secure-attribut</translation-key>ten.','Backend / Library / Navigation<translation-key id="Compatibility-Patches">Compatibility Patches</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Compatibility-Patches">Kompatibilitetsrettelser</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextExample: if the website operates under <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong>, no cookie associated with <strong><em>example.com</em></strong> can be deleted.'=>'Eksempel: hvis hjemmesiden opererer under <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong>er der ingen cookie forbundet med <strong><em>example.com</em></strong> kan slettes.','Backend / Library / Navigation<translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Content Blockers</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Indholdsblokkere</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextNamed cookies will be only set after consent by the visitor was given and the website was reloaded.'=>'Navngivne cookies vil kun blive sat, når den besøgende har givet sit samtykke, og hjemmesiden er blevet genindlæst.','Backend / Library / NavigationInstalled Packages'=>'Installerede pakker','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Block-Cookies-Before-Consent">Block Cookies Before Consent</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Block-Cookies-Before-Consent">Blokér cookies før samtykke</translation-key>','Backend / Library / Navigation<translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Script Blockers</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Scriptblokkere</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Prioritize">Prioritize</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Prioritize">Prioritér</translation-key>','Backend / Library / Navigation<translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Services">Servicer</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> information?'=>'Hvad er formålet med oplysninger om <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyder</translation-key>?','Backend / Library / Navigation<translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Stilblokkere</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineOpt-out Shortcode explained'=>'Opt-out-shortcode forklaret','Backend / Library / Input PlaceholderSearch'=>'Søg','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> explained'=>'<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> forklaret','Backend / Library / Table HeadlineType'=>'Type','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> can be used to display an opt-out option for this <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcoden</translation-key> kan bruges til at vise en mulighed for opt-out for denne <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Library / Table HeadlineName'=>'Navn','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> is loaded in <strong><em>&lt;head&gt;</em></strong> and is executed before the page is fully loaded.'=>'<translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in-koden</translation-key> er indlæst i <strong><em>&lt;head&gt;</em></strong> og udføres, før siden er fuldt indlæst.','Backend / Library / Table HeadlineStatus'=>'Status','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThis function cannot be combined with unblock code from a <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'Denne funktion kan ikke kombineres med kode, der fjerner blokeringen af en<translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokker</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Scriptblokker</translation-key> eller <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Stilblokker</translation-key>.','Backend / Library / TextAre you sure you want to uninstall the package?'=>'Er du sikker på, at du vil afinstallere pakken?','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextFor legal compliance, every <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> must be linked to a specific <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>.'=>'For at overholde lovgivningen skal hver <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> være knyttet til en bestemt <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyder</translation-key>.','Backend / Library / TextPackage'=>'Pakke','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextIn the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> section (found under <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Consent Management</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Providers">Providers</translation-key>), you will find more information and also have the option to edit or create new <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> entries.'=>'I sektionen <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyder</translation-key> (findes under <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Samtykkehåndtering</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Providers">Udbydere</translation-key>) finder du flere oplysninger og har også mulighed for at redigere eller oprette nye <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyder</translation-key>-poster.','Backend / Library / TextRecommended'=>'Anbefalet','Backend / License / Alert MessagePlease activate your license key first. <a href="?page=borlabs-cookie-license">Click here</a> to enter your license key.'=>'Aktivér din licensnøgle først. <a href="?page=borlabs-cookie-license">Klik her</a> for at indtaste din licensnøgle.','Backend / License / Alert MessagePlease enter your license key to receive updates.'=>'Indtast din licensnøgle for at modtage opdateringer.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> can be used to execute custom code associated with this type of <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> once the visitor has given consent to the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. This can be used, for example, to block a conversion pixel code.'=>'<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcoden</translation-key> kan bruges til at udføre tilpasset kode, der er forbundet med denne type <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>, når den besøgende har givet samtykke til <translation-key id="Service">Servicen</translation-key>. Dette kan f.eks. bruges til at blokere en konverteringspixelkode.','Backend / License / Alert MessageYour license key is not valid.'=>'Din licensnøgle er ikke gyldig.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> for example can be used in the <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Meta Box</translation-key> of <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. You can find it for example in <translation-key id="Posts">Posts</translation-key> &raquo; <em><translation-key id="Your-Post">Your Post</translation-key></em> &raquo; <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Custom-Code">Custom Code</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcoden</translation-key> kan for eksempel bruges i <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Metaboksen</translation-key> i <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. Du kan f.eks. finde den i <translation-key id="Posts">Indlæg</translation-key> &raquo; <em><translation-key id="Your-Post">Dit indlæg</translation-key></em> &raquo; <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Custom-Code">Tilpasset kode</translation-key>.','Backend / License / Alert MessageYour license request is not valid.'=>'Din licensanmodning er ikke gyldig.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcodes</translation-key> are not available until the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is created.'=>'<translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcodesene</translation-key> er ikke tilgængelige, før <translation-key id="Service">Servicen</translation-key> er oprettet.','Backend / Services / LabelAsynchronous Opt-out Code'=>'Asynkron opt-out-kode','Backend / Services / LabelBlock Cookies Before Consent'=>'Blokér cookies før samtykke','Backend / Services / Label<translation-key id="Prioritize">Prioritize</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Prioritize">Prioritér</translation-key>','Backend / Services / HintThe <translation-key id="Opt-out-Code">Opt-out Code</translation-key> contains asynchronous JavaScript code that needs to executed to finish the Opt-out.'=>'<translation-key id="Opt-out-Code">Opt-out-koden</translation-key> indeholder asynkron JavaScript-kode, der skal udføres for at afslutte opt-out.','Backend / Services / HintIf enabled, <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> tries to block cookies with the names from <translation-key id="Cookie-Name">Cookie Name</translation-key> until consent is given.'=>'Hvis aktiveret forsøger <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>at blokere cookies med navnene fra <translation-key id="Cookie-Name">Cookienavn</translation-key>, indtil der er givet samtykke.','Backend / License / Alert MessageLicense information refreshed successfully.'=>'Oplysningerne om licensen er blevet succesfuldt opdateret.','Backend / Services / HintThe <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> is loaded in <strong><em>&lt;head&gt;</em></strong> and is executed before the page is fully loaded.'=>'<translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in-koden</translation-key> er indlæst i <strong><em>&lt;head&gt;</em></strong> og udføres, før siden er fuldt indlæst.','Backend / License / Alert MessageLicense registered successfully.'=>'Licens succesfuldt registreret.','Backend / Service Location / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Location">Location</translation-key> configured.'=>'Ingen <translation-key id="Location">Adresse</translation-key> konfigureret.','Backend / License / Alert MessageLicense removed successfully.'=>'Licens succesfuldt fjernet.','Backend / Service Location / ButtonAdd Location'=>'Tilføj adresse','Backend / Service Location / LabelHostname'=>'Værtsnavn','Backend / License / BreadcrumbLicense'=>'Licens','Backend / Service Location / LabelPath'=>'Sti','Backend / License / Button TitleRefresh License Information'=>'Opdatér licensoplysninger','Backend / Service Location / Headline<translation-key id="Locations">Locations</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Locations">Adresser</translation-key>','Backend / License / Button TitleRemove License'=>'Fjern licens','Backend / Service Location / Table HeadlineHostname'=>'Værtsnavn','Backend / License / LabelCloud Scans'=>'Cloudscanninger','Backend / Service Location / Table HeadlinePath'=>'Sti','Backend / License / LabelConfirm Refresh'=>'Bekræft opdatering','Backend / Service Location / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is a <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key>?'=>'Hvad er et <translation-key id="Hostname">Værtsnavn</translation-key>?','Backend / License / LabelLicense Key'=>'Licensnøgle','Backend / Service Location / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Locations">Locations</translation-key> section?'=>'Hvad er formålet med sektionen <translation-key id="Locations">Adresser</translation-key>?','Backend / License / LabelLicense Name'=>'Licensnavn','Backend / Service Location / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key> is the domain name of the website. For example, if the URL of the website is <strong><em>https://www.example.com</em></strong>, the <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key> is <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong>.'=>'<translation-key id="Hostname">Værtsnavnet</translation-key> er hjemmesidens domænenavn. Hvis hjemmesidens URL f.eks. er <strong><em>https://www.example.com</em></strong>, så er <translation-key id="Hostname">Værtsnavnet</translation-key> <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong>.','Backend / License / LabelLicense Status'=>'Licensstatus','Backend / Service Location / Things to know / TextIt may happen that an embedded <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> on your website does not set a cookie, but a connection to a foreign domain is established. Therefore, it is advisable to record this domain here and thus name the service responsible for it, so that interested visitors can understand why this external connection occurs.'=>'Det kan ske, at en indlejret <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> på din hjemmeside ikke sætter en cookie, men at der oprettes en forbindelse til et fremmed domæne. Derfor er det tilrådeligt at registrere dette domæne her og dermed navngive den service, der er ansvarlig for det, så interesserede besøgende kan forstå, hvorfor denne eksterne forbindelse opstår.','Backend / License / LabelValid Until'=>'Gyldig indtil','Backend / Service Option / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Option">Option</translation-key> configured.'=>'Ingen <translation-key id="Option">Valgmulighed</translation-key> konfigureret.','Backend / License / LabelMax Websites'=>'Maksimale antal hjemmesider','Backend / Service Option / ButtonAdd Option'=>'Tilføj valgmulighed','Backend / License / LabelRefresh'=>'Opdatering','Backend / Service Option / LabelDescription'=>'Beskrivelse','Backend / License / Headline<translation-key id="Remove-License">Remove License</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Remove-License">Fjern licens</translation-key>','Backend / Service Option / Headline<translation-key id="Options">Options</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Options">Valgmuligheder</translation-key>','Backend / License / HeadlineYour License'=>'Din licens','Backend / Service Option / Table HeadlineDescription'=>'Beskrivelse','Backend / License / HeadlineYour License Information'=>'Dine licensoplysninger','Backend / Service Option / Table Headline<translation-key id="Type">Type</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Type">Type</translation-key>','Backend / License / HintEnter your License Key.'=>'Indtast din licensnøgle.','Backend / Service Option / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Options">Options</translation-key> section?'=>'Hvad er formålet med sektionen <translation-key id="Options">Valgmuligheder</translation-key>?','Backend / License / HintPlease confirm that you want to remove your license data from this website. After the license data is removed you are able to enter your new license key.'=>'Bekræft, at du ønsker at fjerne dine licensdata fra denne hjemmeside. Når licensdataene er fjernet, kan du indtaste din nye licensnøgle.','Backend / Service Option / Things to know / TextWith <translation-key id="Options">Options</translation-key> you can provide more information about the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. There are six <translation-key id="Types">Types</translation-key> to choose from and you can add as many <translation-key id="Options">Options</translation-key> as you like.'=>'Med <translation-key id="Options">Valgmuligheder</translation-key> kan du give flere oplysninger om <translation-key id="Service">Servicen</translation-key>. Der er seks <translation-key id="Types">Typer</translation-key> at vælge imellem, og du kan tilføje så mange <translation-key id="Options">Valgmuligheder</translation-key>, som du vil.','Backend / License / TextYour license has expired.'=>'Din licens er udløbet.','Backend / Service Option / Things to know / TextFor example, you could select the &quot;<translation-key id="Location-Processing">Location Processing</translation-key>&quot; <translation-key id="Type">Type</translation-key> and add <strong>United States of America</strong> as description if the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> processes data in the United States.'=>'Du kan f.eks. vælge <translation-key id="Type">Typen</translation-key> &quot;<translation-key id="Location-Processing">Dataplacering</translation-key>&quot; og tilføje <strong>USA</strong> som beskrivelse, hvis <translation-key id="Service">Servicen</translation-key> behandler data i USA.','Backend / License / TextYour license is valid.'=>'Din licens er gyldig.','Backend / Services / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> configured.'=>'Ingen <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> konfigureret.','Backend / License / Things to know / HeadlineTransferring a license key to a new website'=>'Overførsel af en licensnøgle til en ny hjemmeside','Backend / License / Things to know / TextYou can use the <translation-key id="Remove-License">Remove License</translation-key> option to remove the license from this website, or you can visit our <translation-key id="Customer-Portal">Customer Portal</translation-key> and remove the license from there.'=>'Du kan bruge indstillingen <translation-key id="Remove-License">Fjern licens</translation-key> til at fjerne licensen fra denne hjemmeside, eller du kan besøge vores <translation-key id="Customer-Portal">Kundeportal</translation-key> og fjerne licensen derfra.','Backend / License / Things to know / Text<a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://service.borlabs.io/" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span><translation-key id="Customer-Portal">Customer Portal</translation-key></span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>'=>'<a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://service.borlabs.io/" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span><translation-key id="Customer-Portal">Kundeportal</translation-key></span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>','Backend / Local Scanner / TextAn error has occurred. Please check your browser\'s console for an error message. If the issue persists even after trying again and switching to <translation-key id="Scan-Mode">Scan Mode</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Manual">Manual</translation-key>, kindly reach out to our support team for assistance.'=>'Der er opstået en fejl. Tjek din browsers konsol for en fejlmeddelelse. Hvis problemet fortsætter, selv efter at du har prøvet igen og skiftet til <translation-key id="Scan-Mode">Scanningstilstand</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Manual">Manuelt</translation-key>, så bedes du kontakte vores supportteam for at få hjælp.','Backend / Services / HeadlineReset Default Services'=>'Nulstil standardservicer','Backend / Local Scanner / ButtonRun scan'=>'Kør scanning','Backend / Services / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset all <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> settings. They will be reset to their default settings. Your custom <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> and the <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> installed via the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key> are not reset.'=>'Bekræft, at du ønsker at nulstille alle indstillinger for <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. De vil blive nulstillet til deres standardindstillinger. Dine tilpassede <translation-key id="Services">Servicer</translation-key> og de <translation-key id="Services">Servicer</translation-key>, der er installeret via <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Biblioteket</translation-key>, bliver ikke nulstillet.','Backend / Local Scanner / LabelPage to scan'=>'Side til scanning','Backend / Services / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Local Scanner / Label<translation-key id="Scan-Mode">Scan Mode</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Scan-Mode">Scanningstilstand</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Table HeadlinePosition'=>'Position','Backend / Local Scanner / Label<translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Search Phrase</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Søgeudtryk</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Table HeadlineStatus'=>'Status','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineScan Progress'=>'Scanningsstatus','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> section?'=>'Hvad er formålet med sektionen <translation-key id="Services">Servicer</translation-key>?','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineScan Settings'=>'Scanningsindstillinger','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Symboler forklaret','Backend / Local Scanner / HintThe string <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> is looking for. Separate multiple entries with a comma.'=>'Den streng, som <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> leder efter. Adskil flere poster med et komma.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextIn the <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> section you can document the use of services and their cookies for your visitors, as well as integrate JavaScripts, such as Google Analytics.'=>'I sektionen <translation-key id="Services">Servicer</translation-key> kan du dokumentere brugen af tjenester og deres cookies for dine besøgende samt integrere JavaScripts, såsom Google Analytics.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextBecause <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> uses the opt-in process, JavaScripts are only executed after the visitor has given their consent to the <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Fordi <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> bruger opt-in-processen, udføres JavaScripts kun, når den besøgende har givet sit samtykke til <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppen</translation-key> eller <translation-key id="Service">Servicen</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Scan-Modes">Scan Modes</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Scan-Modes">Scanningstilstande</translation-key>','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is active and displayed in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>. Not available for the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Service">Servicen</translation-key> er aktiv og vises i <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key>. Ikke tilgængelig for <translation-key id="Service">Servicen</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Current-User">Current User</translation-key>:<br>The scan is performed as the currently logged in user. This may affect the results if the user has different rights than a guest user.'=>'<translation-key id="Current-User">Nuværende bruger</translation-key>:<br>Scanningen udføres som den nuværende indloggede bruger. Dette kan påvirke resultaterne, hvis brugeren har andre rettigheder end en gæstebruger.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextDelete the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. Not available for the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.'=>'Slet <translation-key id="Service">Servicen</translation-key>. Ikke tilgængelig for <translation-key id="Service">Servicen</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineFor example: Some plugins do not embed tracking JavaScript for users with the role of an administrator.'=>'For eksempel: Nogle plugins indlejrer ikke JavaScript til sporing for brugere med rollen som administrator.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextEdit the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Redigér <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Guest">Guest</translation-key>:<br>The scan is performed as a guest user. This is the default setting.'=>'<translation-key id="Guest">Gæst</translation-key>:<br>Scanningen udføres som gæstebruger. Dette er standardindstillingen.','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is inactive and not displayed in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>. Not available for the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Service">Servicen</translation-key> er inaktiv og vises ikke i <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key>. Ikke tilgængelig for <translation-key id="Service">Servicen</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Manual">Manual</translation-key>:<br>When you use this mode, a signed URL is provided that you can use to run the scan by clicking on it. This is useful if the scan cannot be performed due to a server configuration or if your website is not accessible from the outside (<translation-key id="Local-Environment">Local Environment</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Staging-Environment">Staging Environment</translation-key>), for example.'=>'<translation-key id="Manual">Manuelt</translation-key>:<br>Når du bruger denne tilstand, leveres en signeret URL, som du kan bruge til at køre scanningen ved at klikke på den. Dette er nyttigt, hvis scanningen ikke kan udføres på grund af en serverkonfiguration, eller hvis din hjemmeside f.eks. ikke er tilgængelig udefra (<translation-key id="Local-Environment">Lokalt miljø</translation-key> eller <translation-key id="Staging-Environment">Staging-miljø</translation-key>).','Backend / Service Group / BreadcrumbEdit: {{ name }}'=>'Redigér: {{ name }}','Backend / Local Scanner / Alert MessageNo scan result available.'=>'Intet scanningsresultat tilgængeligt.','Backend / Service Group / BreadcrumbService Groups'=>'Servicegrupper','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Matched-Handles">Matched Handles</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Matched-Handles">Matchede handles</translation-key>','Backend / Service Group / BreadcrumbNew'=>'Ny','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Matched-Tags">Matched Tags</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Matched-Tags">Matchede tags</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / LabelDescription'=>'Beskrivelse','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Unmatched-Handles">Unmatched Handles</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Unmatched-Handles">Ikke-matchede handles</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / LabelID'=>'ID','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Unmatched-Tags">Unmatched Tags</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Unmatched-Tags">Ikke-matchede tags</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / LabelName'=>'Navn','Backend / Local Scanner / HintSpecifies the name of the object that must be present for the script from the <strong>Tag</strong> column to be executed. Allowed characters include $, _, letters (both upper and lower case), and numbers. The first character must be $, _, or a letter, while subsequent characters can also include numbers.'=>'Angiver navnet på det objekt, der skal være til stede, for at scriptet fra kolonnen <strong>Tag</strong> kan udføres. Tilladte tegn omfatter $, _, bogstaver (både store og små) og tal. Det første tegn skal være $, _ eller et bogstav, mens de efterfølgende tegn også kan omfatte tal.','Backend / Service Groups / LabelPosition'=>'Position','Backend / Local Scanner / HintEnter a unique string found in the <strong>Tag</strong> to block the script. It should be unique enough that it is not found in other JavaScripts as well.'=>'Indtast en unik streng, der findes i det <strong>Tag</strong>, der skal blokere scriptet. Den skal være så unik, at den ikke også findes i andre JavaScripts.','Backend / Service Groups / LabelPre-selected'=>'Forudvalgt','Backend / Local Scanner / Table HeadlineBlock'=>'Blok','Backend / Service Groups / Label<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key>','Backend / Local Scanner / Table Headline<translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / LabelStatus'=>'Status','Backend / Local Scanner / Table Headline<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / HeadlineService Group Information'=>'Servicegruppeoplysninger','Backend / Local Scanner / Table Headline<translation-key id="Phrase">Phrase</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Phrase">Udtryk</translation-key>','Backend / Service Groups / HeadlineService Group Settings'=>'Servicegruppeindstillinger','Backend / Local Scanner / Table HeadlineTag'=>'Tag','Backend / Service Groups / HintEnter a description for this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>. It is displayed to the visitor in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'Indtast en beskrivelse af denne <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppe</translation-key>. Den vises for den besøgende i <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Table HeadlineType'=>'Type','Backend / Service Groups / Hint<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be set. The <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be at least 3 characters long and may only contain: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>'=>'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> skal være indstillet. <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key>\'et skal være mindst tre tegn langt og må kun indeholde: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>','Backend / Local Scanner / Table HeadlineURL'=>'URL','Backend / Service Groups / HintChoose a name for this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>. It is displayed to the visitor in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'Vælg et navn til denne <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppe</translation-key>. Det vises for den besøgende i <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> are used to identify the JavaScript files that are loaded on your website. For example, your installed <translation-key id="Themes">Themes</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> use the WordPress function <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://developer.wordpress.org/reference/functions/wp_enqueue_script/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><strong><em>wp_enqueue_script()</em></strong><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> to define the <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> bruges til at identificere de JavaScript-filer, der indlæses på din hjemmeside. For eksempel bruger dine installerede <translation-key id="Themes">Temaer</translation-key> og <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> WordPress-funktionen <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://developer.wordpress.org/reference/functions/wp_enqueue_script/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><strong><em>wp_enqueue_script()</em></strong><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> til at definere <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Groups / HintDetermine the position where this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> is displayed. Order follows natural numbers.'=>'Bestem den position, hvor denne <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppe</translation-key> vises. Rækkefølgen følger naturlige tal.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> are used to identify the <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> files that are loaded on your website. For example, your installed <translation-key id="Themes">Themes</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> use the WordPress function <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://developer.wordpress.org/reference/functions/wp_enqueue_style/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><strong><em>wp_enqueue_style()</em></strong><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> to define the <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> bruges til at identificere de <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key>-filer, der indlæses på din hjemmeside. For eksempel bruger dine installerede <translation-key id="Themes">Temaer</translation-key> og <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> WordPress-funktionen <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="https://developer.wordpress.org/reference/functions/wp_enqueue_style/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><strong><em>wp_enqueue_style()</em></strong><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a> til at definere <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Groups / HintIf enabled, this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> is pre-selected in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>. The visitor can de-select it.'=>'Hvis den er aktiveret, er denne <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppe</translation-key> forvalgt i <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key>. Den besøgende kan fravælge den.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Matched-Handles">Matched Handles</translation-key>:<br>These are <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> that matches your <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Search Phrase</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Matched-Handles">Matchede handles</translation-key>:<br>Dette er <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>, der matcher dit <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Søgeudtryk</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Groups / HintUse this <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> to unblock JavaScript or content when user opted-in for this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>.'=>'Brug denne <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> til at fjerne blokeringen af JavaScript eller indhold, når brugeren har valgt denne <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppe</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Unmatched-Handles">Unmatched Handles</translation-key>:<br>These are <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> that do not match a <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Search Phrase</translation-key> but were found during the scan and maybe relevant.'=>'Ikke-matchede <translation-key id="Unmatched-Handles">Ikke-matchede handles</translation-key>:<br>Dette er <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>, der ikke matcher et <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Søgeudtryk</translation-key>, men som blev fundet under scanningen og er måske relevant.','Backend / Service Groups / HintThe status of this <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>. If enabled it is displayed to the visitor in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'Status for denne <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppe</translation-key>. Hvis den er aktiveret, vises den for den besøgende i <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> explained'=>'<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> forklaret','Backend / Service Groups / Input Placeholder...block this...'=>'... blokér dette ...','Backend / Local Scanner / Things to know / HeadlineInput fields explained'=>'Inputfelter forklaret','Backend / Service Groups / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> explained'=>'<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> forklaret','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> explained'=>'<translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> forklaret','Backend / Services / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> can be used to execute custom code once the visitor has given consent to a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> associated with this type of <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>. This can be used, for example, to block a conversion pixel code.'=>'<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcoden</translation-key> kan bruges til at udføre tilpasset kode, når den besøgende har givet samtykke til en <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>, der er tilknyttet denne type <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppe</translation-key>. Dette kan f.eks. bruges til at blokere en konverteringspixelkode.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> refer to <strong><em>&lt;script&gt;</em></strong> tags that lack an associated <translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key>, which can occur when JavaScript is embedded directly into your website\'s HTML code, bypassing the dedicated WordPress function typically used for this purpose.'=>'<translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> henviser til <strong><em>&lt;script&gt;</em></strong> tags, der mangler et tilknyttet <translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key>, hvilket kan forekomme, når JavaScript er indlejret direkte i din hjemmesides HTML-kode uden om den dedikerede WordPress-funktion, der typisk bruges til dette formål','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> refer to <strong><em>&lt;link&gt;</em></strong> tags and <strong><em>&lt;style&gt;</em></strong> tags that lack an associated <translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key>, which can occur when <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> is embedded directly into your website\'s HTML code, bypassing the dedicated WordPress function typically used for this purpose.'=>'<translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> henviser til <strong><em>&lt;link&gt;</em></strong> Tags og <strong><em>&lt;stil&gt;</em></strong> tags, der mangler et tilknyttet <translation-key id="Handle">Handle</translation-key>, hvilket kan forekomme, når <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> er indlejret direkte i din hjemmesides HTML-kode uden om den dedikerede WordPress-funktion, der typisk bruges til dette formål','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Matched-Tags">Matched Tags</translation-key>:<br>These are <translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> that matches your <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Search Phrase</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Matched-Tags">Matchede tags</translation-key>:<br>Dette er <translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key>, der matcher dit <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Søgeudtryk</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Unmatched-Tags">Unmatched Tags</translation-key>:<br>These are <translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key> that do not match a <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Search Phrase</translation-key> but were found during the scan and maybe relevant.'=>'<translation-key id="Unmatched-Tags">Ikke-matchede tags</translation-key>:<br>Dette er <translation-key id="Tags">Tags</translation-key>, der ikke matcher et <translation-key id="Search-Phrase">Søgeudtryk</translation-key>, men som blev fundet under scanningen og måske er relevant.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Phrase">Phrase</translation-key>:<br>Enter a unique string found in the <strong>Tag</strong> to block the script. It should be unique enough that it is not found in other JavaScripts as well.'=>'<translation-key id="Phrase">Udtryk</translation-key>:<br>Indtast en unik streng, der findes i det <strong>Tag</strong>, der skal blokere scriptet. Den skal være så unik, at den ikke også findes i andre JavaScripts.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>:<br>This feature is optional and ensures that once the JavaScript is unblocked, it does not execute until the object specified in the <translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key> column is present on the website. This capability facilitates the resolution of race condition issues.'=>'<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>:<br>Denne funktion er valgfri og sikrer, at når JavaScript ikke længere blokeres, udføres det ikke, før objektet, der er angivet i <translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>, er til stede på hjemmesiden. Denne funktion gør det lettere at løse problemer med race condition.','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineSpecifies the name of the object that must be present for the script from the <strong>Tag</strong> column to be executed. Allowed characters include $, _, letters (both upper and lower case), and numbers. The first character must be $, _, or a letter, while subsequent characters can also include numbers.'=>'Angiver navnet på det objekt, der skal være til stede, for at scriptet fra kolonnen <strong>Tag</strong> kan udføres. Tilladte tegn omfatter $, _, bogstaver (både store og små) og tal. Det første tegn skal være $, _ eller et bogstav, mens de efterfølgende tegn også kan omfatte tal.','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineExample:'=>'For eksempel:','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineThe example initiates loading an external library and concurrently calls the <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> function. This could induce a race condition issue since, when <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> is invoked, the <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong> library—responsible for providing this method—might not yet be fully loaded.'=>'Eksemplet påbegynder indlæsning af et eksternt bibliotek og kalder samtidig <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong>-funktionen. Dette kan fremkalde et race condition-problem, fordi når <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> påkaldes, så vil <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong>-biblioteket, der er ansvarlig for at udbyde denne metode, måske endnu ikke være fuldt indlæst.','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineTo mitigate this race condition, block both the script tag that loads the <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong> library and the script tag that calls <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong>. For the script tag where <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> is called, enter <strong><em>calendarLibrary</em></strong> in the <translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key> field.'=>'For at afbøde denne race condition skal du blokere både det script tag, der indlæser <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong>-biblioteket og det script tag, der kalder <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong>. For script tagget, hvor <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> kaldes, skal du indtaste <strong><em>kalenderBibliotek</em></strong> i feltet <translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>.','Backend / Local Scanner / HeadlineIf the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is now unblocked, the script-tag containing <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong> will not execute until the <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong> has completely loaded.'=>'Hvis <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Scriptblokkeren</translation-key> ikke længere blokeres, vil script-tagget, der indeholder <strong><em>calendarLibrary.init()</em></strong>, ikke vil blive udført, før <strong><em>calendar-library.js</em></strong> er helt indlæst.','Backend / Local Scanner / Headline<translation-key id="Phrase">Phrase</translation-key>:<br>Enter a unique string found in the <strong>Tag</strong> to block the <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key>. It should be unique enough that it is not found in other <strong><em>&lt;link&gt;</em></strong> tags or <strong><em>&lt;style&gt;</em></strong> tags as well.'=>'<translation-key id="Phrase">Udtryk</translation-key>:<br>Indtast en unik streng, der findes i den <strong>Tag</strong>, der skal blokere <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key>\'en. Den skal være så unik, at den ikke findes i andre <strong><em>&lt;link&gt;</em></strong> tags eller <strong><em>&lt;stil&gt;</em></strong> tags.','Backend / Local Scanner / ValidationThe phrase is not found in the JavaScript code on the left side.'=>'Udtrykket findes ikke i JavaScript-koden i venstre side.','Backend / Local Scanner / ValidationThe phrase is not unique and overlaps with a phrase for another JavaScript.'=>'Udtrykket er ikke unikt og overlapper med et udtryk for et andet JavaScript.','Backend / Log / Alert MessageThe <translation-key id="Log">Log</translation-key> could not be found.'=>'<translation-key id="Log">Logfilen</translation-key> kunne ikke findes.','Backend / Log / Breadcrumb<translation-key id="Logs">Logs</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Logs">Logfiler</translation-key>','Backend / Log / BreadcrumbDetails'=>'Oplysninger','Backend / Log / HeadlineProcess History'=>'Proceshistorik','Backend / Log / FieldBacktrace'=>'Tilbagesporing','Backend / Log / FieldContext'=>'Sammenhæng','Backend / Log / FieldLevel'=>'Niveau','Backend / Log / FieldMessage'=>'Besked','Backend / Log / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Logs">Logs</translation-key> found.'=>'Ingen <translation-key id="Logs">Logfiler</translation-key> fundet.','Backend / Log / Headline<translation-key id="Logs">Logs</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Logs">Logfiler</translation-key>','Backend / Log / PlaceholderSearch Process ID, Level or Message'=>'Søg på proces-id, niveau eller besked','Backend / Log / Table HeadlineHas backtrace'=>'Har tilbagesporing','Backend / Log / Table HeadlineHas context'=>'Har kontekst','Backend / Log / Table HeadlineCreated at'=>'Oprettet den','Backend / Log / Table HeadlineLevel'=>'Niveau','Backend / Log / Table HeadlineMessage'=>'Besked','Backend / MetaBox / Field<translation-key id="Custom-Code">Custom Code</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Custom-Code">Tilpasset kode</translation-key>','Backend / MetaBox / HeadlineBorlabs Cookie - Meta Box'=>'Borlabs Cookie - Metaboks','Backend / MetaBox / HintThe code you enter here will only run on this page. Extend your code by wrapping it with our blocking <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcodes</translation-key> to ensure that it only executes after you\'ve received consent. This functionality proves useful in scenarios such as needing to trigger a conversion pixel exclusively on this page.'=>'Koden, du indtaster her, vil kun køre på denne side. Udvid din kode ved at pakke den ind i vores blokerende <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcodes</translation-key> for at sikre, at den kun udføres, når du har modtaget samtykke. Denne funktion er nyttig i scenarier, hvor du f.eks. har brug for at udløse en konverteringspixel udelukkende på denne side.','Backend / Providers / BreadcrumbEdit: {{ name }}'=>'Redigér: {{ name }}','Backend / Providers / BreadcrumbProviders'=>'Udbydere','Backend / Providers / BreadcrumbNew'=>'Ny','Backend / Providers / LabelAddress'=>'Adresse','Backend / Providers / LabelCookie URL'=>'Cookie URL','Backend / Providers / LabelDescription'=>'Beskrivelse','Backend / Providers / Label<translation-key id="IAB-Vendor-ID">IAB Vendor ID</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="IAB-Vendor-ID">Id for IAB-leverandør</translation-key>','Backend / Providers / LabelID'=>'ID','Backend / Providers / LabelName'=>'Navn','Backend / Providers / LabelOpt-out URL'=>'Opt-out-URL','Backend / Providers / LabelPartners'=>'Partnere','Backend / Providers / Label<translation-key id="Privacy-Url">Privacy URL</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Privacy-Url">URL til privatlivspolitik</translation-key>','Backend / Providers / HeadlineProvider Information'=>'Udbyderoplysninger','Backend / Providers / LabelYou can optionally provide the <translation-key id="IAB-Vendor-ID">IAB Vendor ID</translation-key> to add information about an IAB Vendor that is not part of the IAB TCF standard.'=>'Du kan eventuelt angive <translation-key id="IAB-Vendor-ID">Id for IAB-leverandør</translation-key> for at tilføje oplysninger om en IAB-leverandør, der ikke er en del af IAB TCF-standarden.','Backend / Providers / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key> section?'=>'Hvad er formålet med sektionen <translation-key id="Providers">Udbydere</translation-key>?','Backend / Providers / Things to know / TextFor legal compliance, every <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> must be linked to a specific <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>.'=>'For at overholde lovgivningen skal hver <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> eller <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokker</translation-key> være knyttet til en bestemt <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyder</translation-key>.','Backend / Providers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> is the company that delivers the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> (e.g., Google Analytics) or the content (e.g., YouTube videos).'=>'<translation-key id="Provider">Udbyderen</translation-key> er den virksomhed, der leverer <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> (f.eks. Google Analytics) eller indholdet (f.eks. YouTube-videoer).','Backend / Providers / Things to know / TextVisitors should receive clear information about the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> responsible for the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> or blocked content.'=>'Besøgende skal modtage klare oplysninger om den <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyder</translation-key>, der er ansvarlig for <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> eller blokeret indhold.','Backend / Providers / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> configured.'=>'Ingen <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyder</translation-key> konfigureret.','Backend / Providers / HeadlineProviders'=>'Udbydere','Backend / Providers / HeadlineReset Default Providers'=>'Nulstil standardudbydere','Backend / Providers / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset the <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key>. They will be reset to their default settings. Your custom <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key> and the <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key> installed via the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key> are not reset.'=>'Bekræft, at du ønsker at nulstille <translation-key id="Providers">Udbydere</translation-key>. De vil blive nulstillet til deres standardindstillinger. Dine tilpassede <translation-key id="Providers">Udbydere</translation-key> og de <translation-key id="Providers">Udbydere</translation-key>, der er installeret via <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Biblioteket</translation-key>, bliver ikke nulstillet.','Backend / Providers / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Providers / Table HeadlineName'=>'Navn','Backend / Providers / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Symboler forklaret','Backend / Providers / Things to know / TextDelete the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>. Not available for the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Owner-of-this-website">Owner of this website</translation-key>.'=>'Slet <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyderen</translation-key>. Ikke tilgængelig for <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyderen</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Owner-of-this-website">Ejer af denne hjemmeside</translation-key>.','Backend / Providers / Things to know / TextEdit the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>.'=>'Redigér <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyderen</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / BreadcrumbEdit: {{ name }}'=>'Redigér: {{ name }}','Backend / Script Blockers / BreadcrumbScript Blockers'=>'Scriptblokkere','Backend / Script Blockers / BreadcrumbNew'=>'Ny','Backend / Script Blockers / Field LabelContent Blocker Global JavaScript'=>'Indholdsblokker global JavaScript','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelHandles'=>'Handles','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelID'=>'ID','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelName'=>'Navn','Backend / Script Blockers / Label<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="onExist">onExist</translation-key>','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelPhrases'=>'Udtryk','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelService Opt-in Script Tag'=>'Service opt-in script tag','Backend / Script Blockers / LabelStatus'=>'Status','Backend / Script Blockers / HeadlineScript Blocker Configuration'=>'Konfiguration af scriptblokker','Backend / Script Blockers / HeadlineScript Blocker Information'=>'Oplysninger om scriptblokker','Backend / Script Blockers / HeadlineScript Blocker Settings'=>'Indstillinger for scriptblokker','Backend / Script Blockers / HintIf your intention is to unblock previously blocked JavaScripts upon unblocking a <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>, please insert the provided JavaScript into the <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> field within your <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> settings.'=>'Hvis din hensigt er at fjerne blokeringen af tidligere blokerede JavaScripts, når du fjerner blokeringen af en <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokker</translation-key>, skal du indsætte det medfølgende JavaScript i feltet <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> i indstillingerne for din <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokker</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / Hint<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be set. The <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be at least 3 characters long and may only contain: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>'=>'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> skal være indstillet. <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key>\'et skal være mindst tre tegn langt og må kun indeholde: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>','Backend / Script Blockers / HintThe name of the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'Navnet på <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Scriptblokkeren</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / HintTo allow the unblocking of previously blocked JavaScripts through user consent for a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>, please insert the ensuing script tag into the field labeled <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> within your <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'For at tillade at blokeringen fjernes af tidligere blokerede JavaScripts gennem brugerens samtykke til en <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>, skal du indsætte det følgende script tag i feltet mærket <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in-kode</translation-key> i din <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / HintThe status of this <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key>. If the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is disabled, it will not block JavaScript.'=>'Status for denne <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Scriptblokker</translation-key>. Hvis <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Scriptblokkeren</translation-key> er deaktiveret, vil den ikke blokere JavaScript.','Backend / Script Blockers / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> configured.'=>'Der er ikke konfigureret nogen <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Scriptblokker</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / HeadlineScript Blockers'=>'Scriptblokkere','Backend / Script Blockers / Table Headline<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>','Backend / Script Blockers / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Script Blockers / Table HeadlineName'=>'Navn','Backend / Script Blockers / Table Headline<translation-key id="On-Exist">onExist</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="On-Exist">onExist</translation-key>','Backend / Script Blockers / Table Headline<translation-key id="Phrases">Phrases</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Phrases">Udtryk</translation-key>','Backend / Script Blockers / Table HeadlineStatus'=>'Status','Backend / Script Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Script Blockers</translation-key> section?'=>'Hvad er formålet med sektionen <translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Scriptblokkere</translation-key>?','Backend / Script Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Symboler forklaret','Backend / Script Blockers / Tip / HeadlineLanguage independent'=>'Uafhængig af sprog','Backend / Script Blockers / Tip / Text<translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Script Blockers</translation-key> are configured independently for all languages.'=>'<translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Scriptblokkere</translation-key> konfigureres uafhængigt af alle sprog.','Backend / Script Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Script Blockers</translation-key> section allows you to block JavaScripts from <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> whose JavaScript you can\'t enter into the <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> field of a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Sektionen <translation-key id="Script-Blockers">Scriptblokkere</translation-key> giver dig mulighed for at blokere JavaScripts fra <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key>, hvis JavaScript du ikke kan indtaste i feltet <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in-kode</translation-key> i en <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / Things to know / TextOnce a <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is created, <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> provides an unblock JavaScript that can be entered into the <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> field of a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. The JavaScript becomes unblocked once a visitor consents to the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Når en <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Scriptblokker</translation-key> er oprettet, leverer <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> et JavaScript, der fjerner blokeringen, og som kan indtastes i feltet <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in-kode</translation-key> i en <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. Blokeringen af JavaScriptet bliver fjernet, når en besøgende samtykker til <translation-key id="Service">Servicen</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / Things to know / TextThis usually allows you to continue using your favorite plugins, but their JavaScript will only run when a visitor gave consent.'=>'Dette giver dig normalt mulighed for at fortsætte med at bruge dine yndlingsplugins, men deres JavaScript kører kun, når en besøgende har givet samtykke.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is enabled and actively prevents JavaScript execution if the <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Phrases">Phrases</translation-key> matches a term configured in the system.'=>'<translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Scriptblokkeren</translation-key> er aktiveret og forhindrer aktivt udførelse af JavaScript, hvis <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> eller <translation-key id="Phrases">Udtryk</translation-key> matcher et udtryk, der er konfigureret i systemet.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextDelete the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key>. Not available for a <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> installed via the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key>.'=>'Slet <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Scriptblokkeren</translation-key>. Ikke tilgængelig for en <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Scriptblokker</translation-key>, der er installeret via <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Biblioteket</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextEdit the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'Redigér <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Scriptblokkeren</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is inactive, allowing all JavaScript to execute without filtering or restricting based on <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Phrases">Phrases</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Scriptblokkeren</translation-key> er inaktiv, så alt JavaScript kan udføres uden filtrering eller begrænsning baseret på <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> eller <translation-key id="Phrases">Udtryk</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Cookie / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Cookie">Cookie</translation-key> configured.'=>'Der er ikke konfigureret nogen <translation-key id="Cookie">Cookie</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Cookie / ButtonAdd Cookie'=>'Tilføj cookie','Backend / Service Cookie / FieldLifetime'=>'Levetid','Backend / Service Cookie / FieldName'=>'Navn','Backend / Service Cookie / HeadlineCookies'=>'Cookies','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlineDescription'=>'Beskrivelse','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlineHostname'=>'Værtsnavn','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlineLifetime'=>'Levetid','Backend / Service Cookie / Table Headline<translation-key id="Name">Name</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Name">Navn</translation-key>','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlinePath'=>'Sti','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlinePurpose'=>'Formål','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlineType'=>'Type','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineYou may input all cookies utilized by the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> here. Typically, information regarding which cookies are used and their respective purposes can be found on the website of the service you intend to add. For instance, details about the cookies used by Google Analytics can be located in its knowledge base.'=>'Du kan indtaste alle cookies, der bruges af <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>, her. Oplysninger om, hvilke cookies der bruges og deres respektive formål, kan typisk findes på hjemmesiden for servicen, du har til hensigt at tilføje. For eksempel kan oplysninger om de cookies, der bruges af Google Analytics, findes i dens vidensbase.','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> section?'=>'Hvad er formålet med sektionen <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key>?','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineInput fields explained'=>'Inputfelter forklaret','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Description">Description</translation-key>: Enter a description of the cookie and explain its purpose. This is optional, but recommended.'=>'<translation-key id="Description">Beskrivelse</translation-key>: Indtast en beskrivelse af cookien og forklar dens formål. Dette er valgfrit, men anbefales.','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineThe <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> section of your browser\'s developer tools can be used to find the values for the <translation-key id="Name">Name</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Path">Path</translation-key>, and <translation-key id="Lifetime">Lifetime</translation-key> fields.'=>'Sektionen <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> i din browsers udviklerværktøjer kan bruges til at finde værdierne for felterne <translation-key id="Name">Navn</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Hostname">Værtsnavn</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Path">Sti</translation-key> og <translation-key id="Lifetime">Levetid</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Lifetime">Lifetime</translation-key>: The field generally matches the <translation-key id="Expires">Expires</translation-key> column in the <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> section of your browser. Inform your visitor how many days the cookie will be stored or enter <translation-key id="Session">Session</translation-key> if the cookie is a session cookie and will be deleted when the browser is closed.'=>'<translation-key id="Lifetime">Levetid</translation-key>: Feltet matcher generelt kolonnen <translation-key id="Expires">Udløber</translation-key> i sektionen <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> i din browser. Fortæl din besøgende, hvor mange dage cookien vil blive gemt, eller skriv <translation-key id="Session">Session</translation-key>, hvis cookien er en sessionscookie og vil blive slettet, når browseren lukkes.','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineIf you find a date in the <translation-key id="Expires">Expires</translation-key> column, this means that the cookie is a persistent cookie and will be deleted on the specified date.'=>'Hvis en dato i kolonnen <translation-key id="Expires">Udløber</translation-key>, betyder det, at cookien er en vedvarende cookie og vil blive slettet på den angivne dato.','Backend / Services / Things to know / HeadlineIf you find the value <translation-key id="Session">Session</translation-key> in the <translation-key id="Expires">Expires</translation-key> column of your browser, this means that the cookie is a session cookie and will be deleted when you close your browser.'=>'Hvis værdien <translation-key id="Session">Session</translation-key> i kolonnen <translation-key id="Expires">Udløber</translation-key> i din browser, betyder det, at cookien er en sessionscookie og vil blive slettet, når du lukker din browser.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key>: The field generally matches the <translation-key id="Domain">Domain</translation-key> column in the <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> section of your browser. You can enter <strong>#</strong> into this field and <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> will display the domain of your website in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Hostname">Værtsnavn</translation-key>: Feltet matcher generelt kolonnen <translation-key id="Domain">Domæne</translation-key> i sektionen <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> i din browser. Du kan indtaste <strong>#</strong> i dette felt, og <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> vil vise domænet for din hjemmeside i <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Name">Name</translation-key>: The field generally matches the <translation-key id="Name">Name</translation-key> column in the <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> section of your browser.'=>'<translation-key id="Name">Navn</translation-key>: Feltet matcher generelt kolonnen <translation-key id="Name">Navn</translation-key> i sektionen <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> i din browser.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Path">Path</translation-key>: The field generally matches the <translation-key id="Path">Path</translation-key> column in the <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> section of your browser. Usually, the path is <strong>/</strong>.'=>'<translation-key id="Path">Sti</translation-key>: Feltet matcher generelt kolonnen <translation-key id="Path">Stien</translation-key> i sektionen <translation-key id="Cookies">Cookies</translation-key> i din browser. Normalt er stien <strong>/</strong>.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Purpose">Purpose</translation-key>: We distinguish in two types of <translation-key id="Purposes">Purposes</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Functional">Functional</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Tracking">Tracking</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="Purpose">Formål</translation-key>: Vi skelner mellem to typer af <translation-key id="Purposes">Formål</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Functional">Funktionelle</translation-key> og <translation-key id="Tracking">Sporing</translation-key>.','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Functional">Functional</translation-key> cookies are required for the basic functionality of the website.'=>'<translation-key id="Functional">Funktionelle</translation-key> cookies er nødvendige for hjemmesidens grundlæggende funktionalitet.','Backend / Country / CountryNorway'=>'Norge','Backend / Library / Button TitleRefresh Library'=>'Opdatér biblioteket','Backend / Country / CountryNepal'=>'Nepal','Backend / Library / Button Title<translation-key id="Button-Reinstall">Reinstall</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Button-Reinstall">Geninstallér</translation-key>','Backend / Country / CountryNauru'=>'Nauru','Backend / Library / Button Title<translation-key id="Button-Uninstall">Uninstall</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Button-Uninstall">Afinstallér</translation-key>','Backend / Country / CountryNiue'=>'Niue','Backend / Library / Button Title<translation-key id="Button-Update">Update</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Button-Update">Opdatér</translation-key>','Backend / Country / CountryNew Zealand'=>'New Zealand','Backend / Library / Description ListBorlabs Service Modification Date'=>'Ændringsdato for Borlabs Service','Backend / Country / CountryOman'=>'Oman','Backend / Library / Description ListInstalled at'=>'Installeret den','Backend / Country / CountryPanama'=>'Panama','Backend / Library / Description ListInstalled Version'=>'Installeret version','Backend / Country / CountryPeru'=>'Peru','Backend / Library / Description ListLatest Version'=>'Seneste version','Backend / Country / CountryFrench Polynesia'=>'Fransk Polynesien','Backend / Library / Description ListType'=>'Type','Backend / Country / CountryPapua New Guinea'=>'Papua Ny Guinea','Backend / Library / Description ListUpdated at'=>'Opdateret den','Backend / Country / CountryPhilippines'=>'Filippinerne','Backend / Library / Description ListUpdate available'=>'Opdatering tilgængelig','Backend / Country / CountryPakistan'=>'Pakistan','Backend / Library / Description ListVersion'=>'Version','Backend / Country / CountryPoland'=>'Polen','Backend / Library / Field<translation-key 