translation-key>. Du kan finde dem senere ved hjælp af den viste nøgle i visningen <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patches">Kompatibilitetsrettelser</translation-key> vis (<translation-key id="Navigation-System">System</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-System-Compatibility-Patches">Kompatibilitetsrettelser</translation-key>).','Backend / Country / CountrySão Tomé and Príncipe'=>'São Tomé og Príncipe','Backend / Library / HintThe <translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Content Blockers</translation-key> are included in this package and are necessary for the proper functioning of this package. They are installed when you click the <translation-key id="Button-Install">Install</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Reinstall">Reinstall</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Update">Update</translation-key> button. You can locate them later using the displayed name and key in the <translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Content Blockers</translation-key> view (<translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers">Blockers</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Content-Blockers">Content Blockers</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Content-Blockers-Manage">Manage</translation-key>).'=>'<translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Indholdsblokkere</translation-key> er inkluderet i denne pakke og er nødvendige for, at denne pakke fungerer korrekt. De installeres, når du klikker på knappen <translation-key id="Button-Install">Installér</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Reinstall">Geninstallér</translation-key> / <translation-key id="Button-Update">Opdatér</translation-key>. Du kan finde dem senere ved hjælp af det viste navn og nøglen i visningen <translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Indholdsblokkere</translation-key> (<translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers">Blokkere</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Content-Blockers">Indholdsblokkere</transla