og','Backend / Global / Footer / URLhttps://borlabs.io/?utm_source=Borlabs+Cookie&amp;utm_medium=Footer+Logo&amp;utm_campaign=Analysis'=>'https://borlabs.io/?utm_source=Borlabs+Cookie&amp;utm_medium=Footer+Logo&amp;utm_campaign=Analysis','Backend / IAB TCF Configure Vendors / Alert MessageThe <translation-key id="Global-Vendor-List">Global Vendor List</translation-key> is not be downloaded. Please go to the IAB TCF settings and download the list.'=>'<translation-key id="Global-Vendor-List">Liste over globale leverandører</translation-key> kan ikke downloades. Gå til IAB TCF-indstillingerne, og download listen.','Backend / IAB TCF Configure Vendors / Alert MessageCurrently, the <translation-key id="Vendors-Preview">Vendors Preview</translation-key> list is empty. This may be because the <translation-key id="Update-Preview">Update Preview</translation-key> button has not been clicked to refresh the list, or because no consent parameters such as <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Purpose">Purpose</translation-key>, <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Feature">Feature</translation-key>, <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Special-Feature">Special Feature</translation-key>, or <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Special-Purpose">Special Purpose</translation-key> have been selected in the have been selected in the <translation-key id="Configure-Vendors">Configure Vendors</translation-key> panel. Please ensure that you\'ve made your selections and clicked <translation-key id="Update-Preview">Update Preview</translation-key> to see them in the <translation-key id="Vendors-Preview">Vendors Preview</translation-key> list.'=>'På nuværende tidspunkt er listen med <translation-key id="Vendors-Preview">Forhåndsvisning af leverandører</translation-key> tom. Det kan skyldes, at der ikke er klikket på knappen <translation-key id="Update-Preview">Opdater forhåndsvisning</translation-key> for at opdatere listen, eller at der ikke er valgt nogen parametre for samtykke som <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Purpose">Formål</translation-key>, <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Feature">Funktion</translation-key>, <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Special-Feature">Særlig funktion</translation-key> eller <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Special-Purpose">Særligt formål</translation-key> i panelet <translation-key id="Configure-Vendors">Konfigurér leverandører</translation-key>. Sørg for, at du har foretaget dine valg og klikket på <translation-key id="Update-Preview">Opdater forhåndsvisning</translation-key> for at se dem på listen over <translation-key id="Vendors-Preview">Forhåndsvisning af leverandører</translation-key>.','Backend / IAB TCF Configure Vendors / BreadcrumbConfigure Vendors'=>'Konfigurér leverandører','Backend / IAB TCF Configure Vendors / BreadcrumbIAB TCF'=>'IAB TCF','Backend / IAB TCF Configure Vendors / ButtonConfigure Vendors'=>'Konfigurér leverandører','Backend / IAB TCF Configure Vendors / ButtonUpdate Preview'=>'Opdater forhåndsvisning','Backend / IAB TCF Configure Vendors / FieldVendor IDs'=>'Leverandør-id\'er','Backend / IAB TCF Configure Vendors / FieldReplace Vendor Configuration'=>'Udskift leverandørens konfiguration','Backend / IAB TCF Configure Vendors / HeadlineConfigure Vendors'=>'Konfigurér leverandører','Backend / IAB TCF Configure Vendors / HeadlineVendors Preview'=>'Forhåndsvisning af leverandører','Backend / IAB TCF Configure Vendors / HintAlternatively, or in addition, you have the option to input the <translation-key id="IDs">IDs</translation-key> of the <translation-key id="Vendors">Vendors</translation-key> you wish to activate. Enter the <translation-key id="Vendor-IDs">Vendor IDs</translation-key> separated by comma.'=>'Alternativt, eller derudover, har du mulighed for at indtaste <translation-key id="IDs">Id</translation-key>\'erne for de <translation-key id="Vendors">Leverandører</translation-key>, du ønsker at aktivere. Indtast <translation-key id="Vendor-IDs">Leverandør-id</translation-key>\'erne adskilt af komma.','Backend / IAB TCF Configure Vendors / HintIf you enable this option, all existing <translation-key id="Vendors">Vendors</translation-key> will be disabled and only <translation-key id="Vendors">Vendors</translation-key> of this configuration will be enabled. If you leave the option disabled, the <translation-key id="Vendors">Vendors</translation-key> of this configuration will be enabled additionally.'=>'Hvis du aktiverer denne mulighed, vil alle eksisterende <translation-key id="Vendors">Leverandører</translation-key> blive deaktiveret, og kun <translation-key id="Vendors">Leverandører</translation-key> i denne konfiguration vil blive aktiveret. Hvis du lader indstillingen være deaktiveret, vil <translation-key id="Vendors">Leverandørerne</translation-key> i denne konfiguration blive aktiveret yderligere.','Backend / IAB TCF Configure Vendors / Things to know<translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Feature">Feature</translation-key> means one of the features of processing personal data used by participants in the Framework that are defined in the Policies or the Specifications used in pursuit of one or several <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Purposes">Purposes</translation-key> for which the user is not given choice separately to the choice afforded regarding the <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Purposes">Purposes</translation-key> for which they are used.'=>'<translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Feature">Funktion</translation-key> betyder en af de funktioner til behandling af personoplysninger, der anvendes af deltagere i det framework, som er beskrevet i politikkerne eller specifikationerne, der anvendes til at forfølge et eller flere <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Purposes">Formål</translation-key>, som brugeren ikke har mulighed for at vælge særskilt i forhold til det valg, der gives med hensyn til de <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Purposes">Formål</translation-key>, som de anvendes til.','Backend / IAB TCF Configure Vendors / Things to know<translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Purpose">Purpose</translation-key> means one of the defined purposes for processing of data, including users\' personal data, by participants in the Framework that are defined in the Policies or the Specifications for which <translation-key id="Vendors">Vendors</translation-key> declare a Legal Basis in the GVL and for which the user is given choice, i.e. to consent or to object depending on the Legal Basis for the processing, by a CMP.'=>'<translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Purpose">Formål</translation-key> betyder et af de angivede formål for databehandling, herunder brugernes personoplysninger, af deltagere i det framework, der er beskrevet i politikkerne eller specifikationerne, for hvilke <translation-key id="Vendors">Leverandører</translation-key> erklærer et retsgrundlag i GVL, og for hvilke brugeren bliver givet et valg, dvs. at samtykke eller at gøre indsigelse afhængigt af retsgrundlaget for behandlingen, af en CMP.','Backend / IAB TCF Configure Vendors / Things to know<translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Special-Feature">Special Feature</translation-key> means one of the features of processing personal data used by participants in the Framework that are defined in the Policies or the Specifications used in pursuit of one or several <translation-key id="Purposes">Purposes</translation-key> for which the user is given the choice to opt-in separately from the choice afforded regarding the <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Purposes">Purposes</translation-key> which they support.'=>'<translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Special-Feature">Særlig funktion</translation-key> betyder en af de funktioner til behandling af personoplysninger, der anvendes af deltagere i det framework, der er defineret i politikkerne eller specifikationer, der anvendes til at forfølge et eller flere <translation-key id="Purposes">Formål</translation-key>, som brugeren får mulighed for at opt-in separat fra det valg, der gives med hensyn til de <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Purposes">Formål</translation-key>, som de støtter.','Backend / IAB TCF Configure Vendors / Things to know<translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Special-Purpose">Special Purpose</translation-key> means one of the defined purposes for processing of data, including users\' personal data, by participants in the Framework that are defined in the Policies or the Specifications for which <translation-key id="Vendors">Vendors</translation-key> declare a Legal Basis in the GVL and for which the user is not given choice by a CMP.'=>'<translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Special-Purpose">Særligt formål</translation-key> betyder et af de beskrevne formål for databehandling, herunder brugernes personoplysninger, af deltagere i det framework, som er defineret i politikkerne eller specifikationerne, for hvilke <translation-key id="Vendors">Leverandører</translation-key> erklærer et juridisk grundlag i GVL, og for hvilke brugeren ikke får valgmuligheder af en CMP.','Backend / IAB TCF Settings / Alert MessageGlobal Vendor List successfully downloaded.'=>'Liste over globale leverandører er blevet downloadet.','Backend / IAB TCF Settings / BreadcrumbIAB TCF - Settings'=>'IAB TCF - Indstillinger','Backend / IAB TCF Settings / ButtonUpdate GVL'=>'Opdatering af GVL','Backend / IAB TCF Settings / FieldGlobal Vendor List (GVL) Status'=>'Status for liste over globale leverandører (GVL)','Backend / IAB TCF Settings / Field<translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Status">IAB TCF Status</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Status">IAB TCF-status</translation-key>','Backend / IAB TCF Settings / HeadlineGeneral Settings'=>'Generelle indstillinger','Backend / Service Groups / HintWhen <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Status">IAB TCF Status</translation-key> is enabled, certain settings will be overridden or bypassed. For instance, your chosen layout (<translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget">Dialog &amp; Widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog-Settings">Settings</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Layout">Layout</translation-key>) will be substituted with a designated IAB TCF layout. Additionally, the widget (<translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget">Dialog &amp; Widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Widget">Widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Show-Widget">Show Widget</translation-key>) will be turned on and cannot be turned off thereafter.'=>'Når <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Status">IAB TCF-status</translation-key> er aktiveret, vil visse indstillinger blive tilsidesat eller omgået. For eksempel vil dit valgte layout (<translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget">Dialogboks og widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog">Dialogboks</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog-Settings">Indstillinger</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Layout">Layout</translation-key>) blive erstattet af et bestemt IAB TCF-layout. Derudover vil widgetten (<translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget">Dialogboks og widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Widget">Widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Show-Widget">Vis widget</translation-key>) blive slået til og kan ikke slås fra igen.','Backend / IAB TCF Settings / TextGlobal Vendor List is downloaded'=>'Liste over globale leverandører er downloadet','Backend / IAB TCF Settings / TextLast check with API'=>'Sidste tjek med API','Backend / IAB TCF Settings / TextGlobal Vendor List was not downloaded'=>'Liste over globale leverandører blev ikke downloadet','Backend / IAB TCF Settings / HintIAB TCF'=>'IAB TCF','Backend / IAB TCF Settings / HintThe IAB Transparency and Consent Framework (TCF) is a technical standard for the digital advertising industry. It is designed to help all parties in the digital advertising chain ensure that they comply with the EU\'s General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and ePrivacy Directive when processing personal data or accessing and/or storing information on a user\'s device, such as cookies, advertising identifiers, device identifiers and other tracking technologies.'=>'The IAB Transparency and Consent Framework (TCF) er en teknisk standard for den digitale reklamebranche. Den er designet til at hjælpe alle parter i den digitale reklamekæde med at sikre, at de overholder EU\'s generelle databeskyttelsesforordning (GDPR) og e-databeskyttelsesdirektivet, når de behandler personoplysninger eller får adgang til og/eller lagrer oplysninger på en brugers enhed, såsom cookies, reklameidentifikatorer, enhedsidentifikatorer og andre sporingsteknologier.','Backend / IAB TCF Vendor Details / Description ListCookie Max Age (Seconds)'=>'Maksimal alder for cookies (sekunder)','Backend / IAB TCF Vendor Details / Description ListData Categories'=>'Datakategorier','Backend / IAB TCF Vendor Details / Description ListDevice Storage Disclosure URL'=>'URL til oplysning om enhedslagring','Backend / IAB TCF Vendor Details / Description ListLegitimate Interests'=>'Legitime interesser','Backend / IAB TCF Vendor Details / Description ListLegitimate Interest Claim URL'=>'URL for krav om legitime interesser','Backend / IAB TCF Vendor Details / Description ListPolicy URL'=>'URL til politik','Backend / IAB TCF Vendor Details / Description ListStandard Data Retention'=>'Standarddataopbevaring','Backend / IAB TCF Vendor Details / Description ListUses Cookies'=>'Bruger cookies','Backend / IAB TCF Vendor Details / Description ListUses Non-Cookie Access'=>'Bruger Tilgængelighed uden cookie','Backend / IAB TCF Vendor Details / TextData Retention'=>'Opbevaring af data','Backend / IAB TCF Vendor Details / TextDays'=>'Dage','Backend / IAB TCF Vendor Details / TextSeconds'=>'Sekunder','Backend / IAB TCF / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Vendor">IAB TCF Vendor</translation-key> configured.'=>'Ingen <translatio