lt'=>'Gå tilbage til scanningsresultatet','Backend / Country / CountryNetherlands'=>'Holland','Backend / Library / Button Title<translation-key id="Button-Install">Install</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Button-Install">Installér</translation-key>','Backend / Dialog Settings / HeadlineLogo Settings'=>'Logoindstillinger','Backend / Dialog Settings / HeadlineReset Dialog General Settings'=>'Nulstil generelle indstillinger for dialogboks','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintIf enabled, the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> is animated.'=>'Hvis aktiveret er <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key> animeret.','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintChoose the <translation-key id="Animation">Animation</translation-key> with which the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> appears.'=>'Vælg <translation-key id="Animation">Animationen</translation-key>, som <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key>vises med.','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintChoose the <translation-key id="Animation">Animation</translation-key> with which the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> disappears.'=>'Vælg den <translation-key id="Animation">Animation</translation-key>, som <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key> forsvinder med.','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintChoose if the <translation-key id="Switch-Button">Switch Button</translation-key> is round (Status: ON) or squared (Status: OFF). You see <translation-key id="Switch-Buttons">Switch Buttons</translation-key> in the dialog for example under the <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> tab.'=>'Vælg, om <translation-key id="Switch-Button">Switch-knap</translation-key>pen skal være rund (Status: TIL) eller firkantet (Status: FRA). Du kan se <translation-key id="Switch-Buttons">Switch-knap</translation-key> i dialogboksen, f.eks. under fanen <translation-key id="Services">Servicer</translation-key>.','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintThe content below the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> will be covered with a backdrop until the visitor has selected an option. The color of the backdrop can be customized under <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget">Dialog &amp; Widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog-Appearance">Appearance</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Dialog-Settings">Dialog - Settings</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Backdrop">Backdrop</translation-key>.'=>'Indholdet under <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key> dækkes af en baggrund, indtil den besøgende har valgt en mulighed. Baggrundens farve kan tilpasses under <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget">Dialogboks og widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog">Dialogboks</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog-Appearance">Udseende</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Dialog-Settings">Dialogboks - Indstillinger</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Backdrop">Baggrund</translation-key>.','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintWhen this setting is enabled, only visitors from the specified countries will see the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'Når denne indstilling er aktiveret, er det kun besøgende fra de angivne lande, der kan se <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key>.','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintIf you are using a caching plugin on your website, enabling this option is essential for enabling <translation-key id="GeoIP-Active">GeoIP Active</translation-key>.'=>'Hvis du bruger et cache-plugin på din hjemmeside, er det vigtigt at aktivere denne mulighed for at aktivere <translation-key id="GeoIP-Active">GeoIP aktiv</translation-key>.','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintAdd one URL per line. The <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> will not be shown on these pages.'=>'Tilføj en URL per linje. <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key> vil ikke blive vist på disse sider.','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintChoose your <translation-key id="Imprint-Page">Imprint Page</translation-key> or add a custom URL.'=>'Vælg din <translation-key id="Imprint-Page">Kontaktside</translation-key>, eller tilføj en tilpasset URL.','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintChoose the <translation-key id="Layout">Layout</translation-key> of the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'Vælg <translation-key id="Layout">Layoutet</translation-key> på <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key>.','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintChoose a <translation-key id="Logo">Logo</translation-key> you want to appear in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'Vælg det <translation-key id="Logo">Logo</translation-key>, du vil have vist i <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key>.','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintChoose the HD version of the <translation-key id="Logo">Logo</translation-key> you want to appear in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>. It will be used for high resolution displays.'=>'Vælg den HD-version af <translation-key id="Logo">Logoet</translation-key>, du vil have vist i <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key>. Den vil blive brugt til skærme med høj opløsning.','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintChoose the <translation-key id="Position">Position</translation-key> in which the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> appears.'=>'Vælg den <translation-key id="Position">Position</translation-key>, hvor <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key> skal vises.','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintChoose your <translation-key id="Privacy-Page">Privacy Page</translation-key> or add a custom URL.'=>'Vælg din <translation-key id="Privacy-Page">Side for privatlivspolitik</translation-key>, eller tilføj en tilpasset URL.','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintRepeat animation.'=>'Gentag animation.','Backend / Dialog Appearance / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset all <translation-key id="Dialog-General">Dialog General</translation-key> settings. They will be reset to their default settings.'=>'Bekræft, at du vil nulstille alle <translation-key id="Dialog-General">Dialogboksens generelle</translation-key> indstillinger. De vil blive nulstillet til deres standardindstillinger.','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintChoose the justification of the <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> items (list items or checkboxes) in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>. Has no effect if the <translation-key id="Layout">Layout</translation-key> is set to <translation-key id="Bar-Slim">Bar - Slim</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Box-Slim">Box - Slim</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Box-Plus">Box - Plus</translation-key>.'=>'Vælg begrundelsen for <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppe</translation-key>-elementer (listeelementer eller afkrydsningsfelter) i <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key>. Har ingen effekt, hvis <translation-key id="Layout">Layout</translation-key> er indstillet til <translation-key id="Bar-Slim">Bar - Slank</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Box-Slim">Boks - Slank</translation-key> eller <translation-key id="Box-Plus">Boks - Plus</translation-key>.','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintIf enabled, the <translation-key id="Accept-All">Accept All</translation-key> button will be shown to the visitor, with which the visitor can accept all <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key>.'=>'Hvis den er aktiveret, vises knappen <translation-key id="Accept-All">Acceptér alle</translation-key> for den besøgende, hvormed den besøgende kan acceptere alle <translation-key id="Services">Servicer</translation-key>.','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintIf enabled, the <translation-key id="Accept-Only-Essential">Accept Only Essential</translation-key> button will be shown to the visitor.'=>'Hvis aktiveret vil knappen <translation-key id="Accept-Only-Essential">Acceptér kun nødvendige</translation-key> blive vist til den besøgende.','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintThe <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> contains a reference to Borlabs Cookie. Activate this option to support this plugin. Thank you very much!<br><br>Please note: if you have enabled the <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Status">IAB TCF Status</translation-key>, an information about the <translation-key id="CMP-ID">CMP ID</translation-key> of <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> is displayed, which cannot be deactivated.'=>'<translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key> indeholder en henvisning til Borlabs Cookie. Aktivér denne mulighed for at støtte dette plugin. Mange tak!<br><br>Bemærk: Hvis du har aktiveret <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Status">IAB TCF-status</translation-key>, vises en information om <translation-key id="CMP-ID">CMP-id</translation-key>\'et for <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>, som ikke kan deaktiveres.','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintIf enabled, the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> is shown, in which the visitor can give their consent preferences.'=>'Hvis det er aktiveret, vises <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key>, hvor den besøgende kan angive sine samtykkepræferencer.','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintIf enabled, the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> is shown on the login page. The option <translation-key id="Show-Dialog">Show Dialog</translation-key> must be enabled.'=>'Hvis den er aktiveret, vises <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key> på loginsiden. Indstillingen <translation-key id="Show-Dialog">Vis dialogboks</translation-key> skal være aktiveret.','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintIf enabled, a separator is displayed below the headline.'=>'Hvis aktiveret vises en separator under overskriften.','Backend / Dialog Settings / HintIf enabled, the selected <translation-key id="Logo">Logo</translation-key> is displayed in the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'Hvis det er aktiveret, vises det valgte <translation-key id="Logo">Logo</translation-key> i <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key>.','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionAttention Seekers'=>'Attention Seekers','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionBouncing Entrances'=>'Hoppende visning','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionBouncing Exits'=>'Bouncing Exits','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionAccept All'=>'Acceptér alle','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionAccept Only Essential'=>'Acceptér kun Nødvendige','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionSave Selection'=>'Gem valg','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionPrivacy Preferences'=>'Privatlivsindstillinger','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionFading Entrances'=>'Udtonende visninger','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionFading Exits'=>'Fading Exits','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionFlippers'=>'Flippers','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionBar'=>'Bar','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionBar - Advanced'=>'Bar - Advanced','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionBar - Slim'=>'Bar - Slim','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionBox'=>'Boks','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionBox - Advanced'=>'Boks - Advanceret','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionBox - Plus'=>'Boks - Plus','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionBox - Slim'=>'Boks - Slank','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionLightspeed'=>'Lightspeed','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionBottom Center'=>'Nederst midt','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionBottom Left'=>'Nederst venstre','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionBottom Right'=>'Nederst højre','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionMiddle Center'=>'Midterste center','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionMiddle Left'=>'Midt venstre','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionMiddle Right'=>'Midt højre','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionTop Center'=>'Øverst midt','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionTop Left'=>'Øverst venstre','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionTop Right'=>'Øverst højre','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionRotating Entrances'=>'Roterende visninger','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionRotating Exits'=>'Rotating Exits','Backend / Dialog Settings / Option<translation-key id="Justification-Around">Around</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Justification-Around">Lige margener</translation-key>','Backend / Dialog Settings / Option<translation-key id="Justification-Between">Between</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Justification-Between">Mellem</translation-key>','Backend / Dialog Settings / Option<translation-key id="Justification-Center">Center</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Justification-Center">I midten</translation-key>','Backend / Dialog Settings / Option<translation-key id="Justification-Left">Left</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Justification-Left">Venstre</translation-key>','Backend / Dialog Settings / Option<translation-key id="Justification-Right">Right</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Justification-Right">Højre</translation-key>','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionSliding Entrances'=>'Glidende visninger','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionSliding Exits'=>'Sliding Exits','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionSpecials'=>'Specials','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionZoom Entrances'=>'Zoomende visninger','Backend / Dialog Settings / OptionZoom Exits'=>'Zoom Exits','Backend / Dialog Settings / TextDatabase is downloaded'=>'Databasen er downloadet','Backend / Dialog Settings / TextDatabase was not downloaded'=>'Databasen blev ikke downloadet','Backend / Dialog Settings / TextDialog hidden'=>'Dialogboks skjult','Backend / Dialog Settings / TextLast Check with API'=>'Sidste tjek med API','Backend / Dialog Settings / TextDialog visible'=>'Dialogboks synlig','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / TextYes, this feature is compatible with caching. To ensure functionality, please enable the <translation-key id="GeoIP-Caching-Mode">GeoIP Caching Mode</translation-key> option.'=>'Ja, denne funktion er kompatibel med caching. For at sikre funktionaliteten skal du aktivere indstillingen <translation-key id="GeoIP-Caching-Mode">GeoIP-cachetilstand</translation-key>','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / Text<translation-key id="GeoIP">GeoIP</translation-key> allows you show the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> only for visitors from some countries (e.g. for EU citizens).'=>'<translation-key id="GeoIP">GeoIP</translation-key> giver dig mulighed for kun at vise <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key> for besøgende fra visse lande (f.eks. for EU-borgere).','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / TextWhat is <translation-key id="GeoIP">GeoIP</translation-key>?'=>'Hvad er <translation-key id="GeoIP">GeoIP</translation-key>?','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / TextIs <translation-key id="GeoIP">GeoIP</translation-key> working if your website uses caching?'=>'Virker <translation-key id="GeoIP">GeoIP</translation-key>, hvis din hjemmeside bruger caching?','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / HeadlineHow can the visitor change the consent?'=>'Hvordan kan den besøgende ændre samtykket?','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / HeadlineHow to display User ID, Consent History and Service &amp; Service Groups Overview.'=>'Sådan vises bruger-id, samtykkehistorik og servicer og oversigt over servicegrupper.','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / HeadlineHow can the visitor perform an opt-out?'=>'Hvordan kan den besøgende udføre en opt-out?','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is <translation-key id="Service-Group-Justification">Service Group Justification</translation-key>?'=>'Hvad er <translation-key id="Service-Group-Justification">Servicegruppebegrundelse</translation-key>?','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / TextTo offer this option, enter the following <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> to your privacy page. This will create a button which reopens the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'For at tilbyde denne mulighed skal du indtaste følgende <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> på din side for privatlivspolitik. Dette skaber en knap, som genåbner <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key>.','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / TextButton'=>'Knap','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / TextLink'=>'Link','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / TextUse the <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> below to display the <translation-key id=User-ID">User ID</translation-key>: {{ shortcode }}'=>'Brug <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcoden</translation-key> nedenfor til at vise <translation-key id=User-ID">Bruger-id</translation-key>: {{ shortcode }}','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / TextUse the <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> below to display the <translation-key id="Consent-History">Consent History</translation-key>: {{ shortcode }}'=>'Brug <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcoden</translation-key> nedenfor til at vise <translation-key id="Consent-History">Samtykkehistorik</translation-key>: {{ shortcode }}','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / TextUse the <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> below to display an overview of all active <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Service Groups</translation-key>: {{ shortcode }}'=>'Brug <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcoden</translation-key> nedenfor til at få vist en oversigt over alle aktive <translation-key id="Services">Servicer</translation-key> og <translation-key id="Service-Groups">Servicegrupper</translation-key>: {{ shortcode }}','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / TextInsert the following <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> to your privacy page. This will create an opt-out button that allows the visitor to opt-out of the specified <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>: {{ shortcode }}'=>'Indsæt følgende <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> på din side for privatlivspolitik. Dette skaber en knap til opt-out, der giver den besøgende mulighed for at opt-out af den angivne <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>: {{ shortcode }}','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / TextYou find the opt-out <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> for each <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> under <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Consent Management</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Services">Services</translation-key>. Click on a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>, and you\'ll find the <translation-key id="Opt-out-Shortcode">Opt-out Shortcode</translation-key>.'=>'Du finder opt-out-<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcoden</translation-key> for hver <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> under <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Samtykkehåndtering</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Services">Servicer</translation-key>. Klik på en <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>, så finder du <translation-key id="Opt-out-Shortcode">Opt-out-shortcoden</translation-key>.','Backend / Dialog Settings / Things to know / Text<translation-key id="Justification-A