r. Dette er teksten på den knap, der bruges til at lukke denne dialogboks.','Backend / Country / CountryGuinea-Bissau'=>'Guinea-Bissau','Backend / Dialog Appearance / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset all <translation-key id="Dialog-Localization">Dialog Localization</translation-key> texts. They will be reset to their default texts.'=>'Bekræft, at du vil nulstille al <translation-key id="Dialog-Localization">Dialogbokslokalisering</translation-key>. De vil blive nulstillet til deres standardtekster.','Backend / Country / CountryGuyana'=>'Guyana','Backend / Dialog Localization / HeadlineWhat is the <translation-key id="IAB-TCF">IAB TCF</translation-key>?'=>'Hvad er <translation-key id="IAB-TCF">IAB TCF</translation-key>?','Backend / Country / CountryHong Kong'=>'Hong Kong','Backend / Dialog Localization / HeadlineLegal Information'=>'Juridisk information','Backend / Country / CountryHeard Island and McDonald Islands'=>'Heard Island og McDonald Islands','Backend / Dialog Localization / HeadlineWhat is the <translation-key id="Dialog-Details">Dialog Details</translation-key>?'=>'Hvad er <translation-key id="Dialog-Details">Dialogboks - Oplysninger</translation-key>?','Backend / Country / CountryHonduras'=>'Honduras','Backend / Dialog Localization / HeadlineWhat is the <translation-key id="Dialog-Entrance">Dialog Entrance</translation-key>?'=>'Hvad er <translation-key id="Dialog-Entrance">Dialogboks - Visning</translation-key>?','Backend / Country / CountryCroatia'=>'Kroatien','Backend / Dialog Localization / TextWhen the <translation-key id="Iab-Tcf-Status">IAB TCF Status</translation-key> setting is enabled (found under <em><translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Consent Management</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Iab-Tcf">IAB TCF</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Iab-Tcf-Settings">Settings</translation-key></em>) the dialog entrance will display these texts instead of the <translation-key id="Legal-Information">Legal Information</translation-key> texts.'=>'Når indstillingen <translation-key id="Iab-Tcf-Status">IAB TCF-status</translation-key> er aktiveret (findes under <em><translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Samtykkehåndtering</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Iab-Tcf">IAB TCF</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Iab-Tcf-Settings">Indstillinger</translation-key></em>), vil dialogboksvisningen vise disse tekster i stedet for teksterne med <translation-key id="Legal-Information">Juridisk information</translation-key>.','Backend / Country / CountryHaiti'=>'Haiti','Backend / Dialog Localization / TextThe dialog <span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">must</span> inform about the topics: '=>'Dialogboksen <span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">skal</span> informere om emnerne: ','Backend / Country / CountryHungary'=>'Ungarn','Backend / Dialog Localization / TextTexts <span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">must</span> also distinguish between <translation-key id="Vendors">Vendors</translation-key> (TCF Standard) and <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key> (Non-TCF Standard).'=>'Tekster <span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">skal</span> også skelne mellem <translation-key id="Vendors">Leverandører</translation-key> (TCF Standard) og <translation-key id="Providers">Udbydere</translation-key> (Non-TCF Standard).','Backend / Country / CountryIndonesia'=>'Indonesien','Backend / Dialog Localization / Text<span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">Warning</span>: Should your modifications infringe upon the IAB\'s TCF standards and we are alerted to a complaint from the IAB, your license will be irrevocably terminated without compensation.'=>'<span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">Advarsel</span>: Hvis dine ændringer krænker IAB\'s TCF-standarder, og vi bliver gjort opmærksom på en klage fra IAB, vil din licens blive uigenkaldeligt opsagt uden kompensation.','Backend / Country / CountryIreland'=>'Irland','Backend / Dialog Localization / TextShould you harbor any uncertainties regarding the compliance of your proposed alterations with the TCF standard, we strongly encourage you to reach out to us prior to implementing any changes.'=>'Hvis du er i tvivl om, hvorvidt dine foreslåede ændringer er i overensstemmelse med TCF-standarden, opfordrer vi dig kraftigt til at kontakte os, før du gennemfører ændringer.','Backend / Country / CountryIsrael'=>'Israel','Backend / Dialog Localization / Text<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Technology">Technology</translation-key>: The technologies used, for example: cookies and their purpose. The number of <translation-key id="Vendors">Vendors</translation-key> <span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">must</span> also be mentioned with the help of <strong><em>{{ totalVendors }}</em></strong>.'=>'<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Technology">Teknologi</translation-key>: De anvendte teknologier, f.eks. cookies og deres formål. Antallet af <translation-key id="Vendors">Leverandører</translation-key> <span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">skal</span> også nævnes ved hjælp af <strong><em>{{ totalVendors }}</em></strong>.','Backend / Country / CountryIsle of Man'=>'Isle of Man','Backend / Dialog Localization / Text<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Personal-Data">Personal Data</translation-key>: What types of personal data are processed?'=>'<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Personal-Data">Personoplysninger</translation-key>: Hvilke typer personoplysninger behandles?','Backend / Country / CountryIndia'=>'Indien','Backend / Dialog Localization / Text<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Legitimate-Interest">Legitimate Interest</translation-key>: You <span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">must</span> inform about the legitimate interest that some <translation-key id="Vendors">Vendors</translation-key> claim for data processing.'=>'<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Legitimate-Interest">Legitime interesser</translation-key>: Du <span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">skal</span> informere om de legitime interesser, som nogle <translation-key id="Vendors">Leverandører</translation-key> påberåber sig i forbindelse med databehandling.','Backend / Country / CountryBritish Indian Ocean Territory'=>'Britisk territorium i Det Indiske Ocean','Backend / Dialog Localization / Text<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-More-Information">More Information</translation-key>: Where the visitor can find more information about the <translation-key id="Vendors">Vendors</translation-key> and the data processed.'=>'<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-More-Information">Flere oplysninger</translation-key>: Hvor den besøgende kan finde flere oplysninger om <translation-key id="Vendors">Leverandører</translation-key> og de data, der behandles.','Backend / Country / CountryIraq'=>'Irak','Backend / Dialog Localization / Text<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-No-Commitment">No Commitment</translation-key>: That the visitor can visit the website without giving consent.'=>'<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-No-Commitment">Ingen forpligtelse</translation-key>: At den besøgende kan besøge hjemmesiden uden at give samtykke.','Backend / Country / CountryIran'=>'Iran','Backend / Dialog Localization / Text<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Revoke">Revoke</translation-key>: That the visitor can revoke the consent any time.'=>'<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Revoke">Tilbagekaldelse</translation-key>: At den besøgende til enhver tid kan tilbagekalde samtykket.','Backend / Country / CountryIceland'=>'Island','Backend / Dialog Localization / Text<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Individual-Settings">Individual Settings</translation-key>: That due to individual settings certain functionalities of the website may be unavailable or operate suboptimally.'=>'<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Individual-Settings">Individuelle indstillinger</translation-key>: At visse funktioner på hjemmesiden på grund af individuelle indstillinger kan være utilgængelige eller ikke fungere optimalt.','Backend / Country / CountryItaly'=>'Italien','Backend / Dialog Localization / TextYou can select which legal information topics you want to show to a visitor.'=>'Du kan vælge, hvilke juridiske informationsemner du vil vise til en besøgende.','Backend / Country / CountryJersey'=>'Jersey','Backend / Dialog Localization / TextIf you disable a text, make sure that its message appears or is part of another text displayed to a visitor.'=>'Hvis du deaktiverer en tekst, skal du sørge for, at dens meddelelse vises, eller at den er en del af en anden tekst, der vises til en besøgende.','Backend / Country / CountryJamaica'=>'Jamaica','Backend / Dialog Localization / TextYou <span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">must</span> inform a visitor about the following topics:'=>'Du <span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">skal</span> informere en besøgende om følgende emner:','Backend / Country / CountryJordan'=>'Jordan','Backend / Dialog Localization / TextA minimum age of 16 is required to consent to non-optional services.'=>'Der kræves en minimumsalder på 16 år for at give samtykke til ikke-valgfrie servicer.','Backend / Country / CountryJapan'=>'Japan','Backend / Dialog Localization / TextThe used technologies, for example: Cookies.'=>'De anvendte teknologier, for eksempel: Cookies.','Backend / Country / CountryKenya'=>'Kenya','Backend / Dialog Localization / TextWhat type of personal data is used and for what purpose.'=>'Hvilke typer personoplysninger bruges og til hvilket formål.','Backend / Country / CountryKyrgyzstan'=>'Kirgisistan','Backend / Dialog Localization / TextWhere more information about each service can be found.'=>'Hvor flere oplysninger om hver service kan findes.','Backend / Country / CountryCambodia'=>'Cambodja','Backend / Dialog Localization / Text<sup>1</sup> That no consent is required to visit your website.'=>'<sup>1</sup> At der ikke kræves noget samtykke for at besøge din hjemmeside.','Backend / Country / CountryKiribati'=>'Kiribati','Backend / Dialog Localization / TextThe visitor can revoke the consent any time.'=>'Den besøgende kan til enhver tid tilbagekalde samtykket.','Backend / Country / CountryComoros'=>'Comorerne','Backend / Dialog Localization / Text<sup>1</sup> What happens when individual settings are applied.'=>'<sup>1</sup> Hvad der sker, når individuelle indstillinger anvendes.','Backend / Country / CountrySt Kitts and Nevis'=>'Saint Kitts og Nevis','Backend / Dialog Localization / Text<sup>2</sup> That personal data can be transferred to non-eu countries with insufficient data protection.'=>'<sup>2</sup> At personoplysninger kan overføres til lande uden for EU med utilstrækkelig databeskyttelse.','Backend / Country / CountryNorth Korea'=>'Nordkorea','Backend / Dialog Localization / Text<sup>1</sup> It is recommended to display this information.'=>'<sup>1</sup> Det anbefales at vise disse oplysninger.','Backend / Country / CountrySouth Korea'=>'Sydkorea','Backend / Dialog Localization / Text<sup>2</sup> You <span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">must</span> display the <translation-key id="Non-EU-Data-Transfer">Non-EU Data Transfer</translation-key> information if you use a service whose company is based in the USA.'=>'<sup>2</sup> Du <span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">skal</span> vise oplysningerne om <translation-key id="Non-EU-Data-Transfer">Dataoverførsel uden for EU</translation-key>, hvis du bruger en service, hvis virksomhed er baseret i USA.','Backend / Country / CountryKuwait'=>'Kuwait','Backend / Dialog Localization / TextThe <translation-key id="Dialog-Entrance">Dialog Entrance</translation-key> is the first thing your visitors see when they visit your website. It is a small dialog that informs your visitors what cookies and services your website uses and that they can change their consent settings in this dialog.'=>'<translation-key id="Dialog-Entrance">Dialogboks - Visning</translation-key> er det første, dine besøgende ser, når de besøger din hjemmeside. Det er en lille dialogboks, der informerer dine besøgende om, hvilke cookies og servicer din hjemmeside bruger, og at de kan ændre deres indstillinger for samtykke i denne dialogboks.','Backend / Country / CountryCayman Islands'=>'Caymanøerne','Backend / Dialog Localization / TextThe <translation-key id="Dialog-Details">Dialog Details</translation-key> is the dialog that opens when your visitors click on the <translation-key id="Individual-Privacy-Preferences">Individual Privacy Preferences</translation-key> button in the <translation-key id="Dialog-Entrance">Dialog Entrance</translation-key>. It contains detailed information about the cookies and services your website uses and allows for more granular consent.'=>'<translation-key id="Dialog-Details">Dialogboks - Oplysninger</translation-key> er den boks, der åbnes, når dine besøgende klikker på knappen <translation-key id="Individual-Privacy-Preferences">Individuelle indstillinger for beskyttelse</translation-key> i <translation-key id="Dialog-Entrance">Dialogboks - Visning</translation-key>. Den indeholder detaljerede oplysninger om de cookies og servicer, din hjemmeside bruger, og giver mulighed for mere opdelt samtykke.','Backend / Country / CountryKazakhstan'=>'Kasakhstan','Backend / Dialog Settings / Alert MessageThe <translation-key id="GeoIP">GeoIP</translation-key> database has been downloaded successfully.'=>'<translation-key id="GeoIP">GeoIP</translation-key>-databasen er blevet succesfuldt downloadet.','Backend / Dialog Settings / Alert MessageDepending on applicable law, this layout may not be allowed to be used.'=>'Afhængigt af gældende lovgivning er det muligvis ikke tilladt at bruge dette layout.','Backend / Dialog Settings / Alert MessageDepending on applicable law, this option may not be allowed to be turned on.'=>'Afhængigt af gældende lovgivning er det muligvis ikke tilladt at slå denne indstilling til.','Backend / Dialog Settings / Alert MessageThe <