key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Consent Management</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Iab-Tcf">IAB TCF</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Iab-Tcf-Settings">Settings</translation-key></em>) this setting influences the visual presentation of the button responsible for showing all vendors.'=>'Når indstillingen <translation-key id="Iab-Tcf-Status">IAB TCF-status</translation-key> er aktiveret (findes under <em><translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Samtykkehåndtering</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Iab-Tcf">IAB TCF</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Iab-Tcf-Settings">Indstillinger</translation-key></em>), påvirker denne indstilling den visuelle præsentation af den knap, der er ansvarlig for at vise alle leverandører.','Backend / Dialog Appearance / HintUsually the theme font is used. To use a custom font family select the checkbox and enter custom font.'=>'Normalt bruges temaets skrifttype. For at bruge en tilpasset skriftfamilie, skal du markere afkrydsningsfeltet og indtaste den tilpassede skrifttype.','Backend / Dialog Appearance / HintThe default padding is defined for <translation-key id="Small-Screen">Small Screen</translation-key>. However, once the viewport width surpasses 640px, the padding specified for <translation-key id="Medium-Screen">Medium Screen</translation-key> will be applied.'=>'Standardpaddingen er angivet for <translation-key id="Small-Screen">Lille skærm</translation-key>. Men når vinduesbredden overstiger 640 px, anvendes paddingen, der er angivet for <translation-key id="Medium-Screen">Medium skærm</translation-key>.','Backend / Dialog Appearance / HintThe separator is exclusively visible on smaller displays, such as smartphones.'=>'Separatoren er udelukkende synlig på mindre skærme, f.eks. på smartphones.','Backend / Dialog Appearance / HintBased on the base font size, the font sizes of all elements are automatically adjusted proportionally.'=>'Baseret på standardskriftstørrelsen justeres skriftstørrelserne på alle elementer automatisk proportionalt.','Backend / Dialog Appearance / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset all <translation-key id="Dialog-Appearance-Settings">Dialog Appearance</translation-key> settings. They will be reset to their default settings.'=>'Bekræft, at du vil nulstille alle indstillinger for <translation-key id="Dialog-Appearance">Dialogboksens udseende</translation-key>. De vil blive nulstillet til deres standardindstillinger.','Backend / Dialog Appearance / Input PlaceholderEnter custom font family'=>'Indtast tilpasset skriftfamilie','Backend / Dialog Appearance / Things to know / TextA <translation-key id="Card">Card</translation-key> displays the name and description of a <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>.'=>'Et <translation-key id="Card">Kort</translation-key> viser navn og beskrivelse af en <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppe</translation-key>.','Backend / Dialog Appearance / Things to know / HeadlineOn which elements do these settings have a visual impact?'=>'Hvilke elementer har disse indstillinger en visuel indvirkning på?','Backend / Dialog Appearance / Things to know / TextA <translation-key id="Card">Card</translation-key> provides a <translation-key id="List">List</translation-key> of <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> associated with the respective <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key>.'=>'Et <translation-key id="Card">Kort</translation-key> indeholder en <translation-key id="List">Liste</translation-key> over <translation-key id="Services">Servicer</translation-key>, der er knyttet til den pågældende <translation-key id="Service-Group">Servicegruppe</translation-key>.','Backend / Dialog Appearance / Things to know / TextClick on the image to see what is affected by these settings.'=>'Klik på billedet for at se, hvad der påvirkes af disse indstillinger.','Backend / Dialog Appearance / Things to know / TextTables are typically located in the details section of a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Provder">Provider</translation-key>, or <translation-key id="Consent-History">Consent History</translation-key>.'=>'Tabeller er typisk placeret i detaljesektionen for en <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Provder">Udbyder</translation-key> eller <translation-key id="Consent-History">Samtykkehistorik</translation-key>.','Backend / Settings / BreadcrumbDialog - Localization'=>'Dialogboks - Lokalisering','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelProvider Dialog - Explanation'=>'Udbyderdialogboks - Forklaring','Seeder / Default Content Blocker / NameDefault'=>'Standard','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelProvider List - Explanation'=>'Liste over udbydere - Forklaring','Seeder / Default Content Blocker / Table HeadlineAccept required service and unblock content'=>'Acceptér påkrævet service, og fjern indholdsblokering','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelService Group List - Explanation'=>'Liste over servicegrupper - Forklaring','Seeder / Default Content Blocker / Button TextYou are currently viewing a placeholder content from <strong>{{ name }}</strong>. To access the actual content, click the button below. Please note that doing so will share data with third-party providers.'=>'Du ser i øjeblikket pladsholderindhold fra <strong>{{ name }}</strong>. Klik på knappen nedenfor for at få adgang til det faktiske indhold. Vær opmærksom på, at dette vil dele data med tredjepartsudbydere.','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelLoading - Text'=>'Indlæsning - Tekst','Seeder / Default Content Blocker / Button TextMore Information'=>'Flere oplysninger','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelNo Consent Data - Text'=>'Ingen samtykkedata - Tekst','Seeder / Default Content Blocker / Button TextUnblock content'=>'Fjern indholdsblokering','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelChoice'=>'Valg','Frontend / Dialog / A11YBelow is a list detailing the provider whose service or content is presently blocked.'=>'Nedenfor er en liste med oplysninger om den udbyder, hvis service eller indhold i øjeblikket er blokeret.','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelConsent given'=>'Samtykke givet','Frontend / Dialog / A11YThe following is a list of providers for whose services consent can be given.'=>'Følgende er en liste over udbydere, hvis servicer der kan gives samtykke til.','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelConsent Withdrawn'=>'Samtykke trukket tilbage','Frontend / Dialog / A11YThe following is a list of service groups for which consent can be given. The first service group is essential and cannot be unchecked.'=>'Følgende er en liste over servicegrupper, som der kan gives samtykke til. Den første servicegruppe er essentiel og kan ikke afkrydses.','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelConsents'=>'Samtykker','Frontend / Consent History / TextConsent History Loading...'=>'Indlæser samtykkehistorik ...','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelDate'=>'Dato','Frontend / Consent History / TextNo Consent Data'=>'Ingen samtykkedata','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelVersion'=>'Version','Frontend / Consent History / TextChoice'=>'Valg','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelChanges'=>'Ændringer','Frontend / Consent History / TextYes'=>'Ja','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelChanges - Added'=>'Ændringer - Tilføjet','Frontend / Consent History / TextNo'=>'Nej','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelChanges - Removed'=>'Ændringer - Fjernet','Frontend / Consent History / Table HeadlineConsents'=>'Samtykker','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelAccept All - Button Text'=>'Acceptér alle - Knaptekst','Frontend / Consent History / Table HeadlineDate'=>'Dato','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelAccept Only Essential - Button Text'=>'Acceptér kun Nødvendige - Knaptekst','Frontend / Consent History / T