leSave'=>'Gem','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelProvider - Tab Title'=>'Udbyder - Fanetitel','Frontend / Dialog / Link TextSelect all'=>'Vælg alle','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelService Group - Tab Title'=>'Servicegruppe - Fanetitel','Frontend / Dialog / Link TextShow Information'=>'Vis oplysninger','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelServices - Tab Title'=>'Servicer - Fanetitel','Frontend / Dialog / Switch Button StatusOn'=>'På','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelPreferences - Button Text'=>'Indstillinger - Knaptekst','Frontend / Dialog / Switch Button StatusOff'=>'Fra','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelPreferences - Link Text'=>'Indstillinger - Linktekst','Frontend / Dialog / TabConsent History'=>'Samtykkehistorik','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelAccessibility - Purpose List - Explanation'=>'Tilgængelighed - Liste over formål - Forklaring','Frontend / Dialog / TabProvider'=>'Udbyder','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelAccessibility - Service Group List - Explanation'=>'Tilgængelighed - Liste over servicegrupper - Forklaring','Frontend / Dialog / TabService Groups'=>'Servicegrupper','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / TextData Retention - Text'=>'Dataopbevaring - Tekst','Frontend / Dialog / TabServices'=>'Servicer','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelStandard Data Retention in Days - Text'=>'Standarddataopbevaring i dage - Tekst','Frontend / Dialog / Button TitleI accept all'=>'Jeg accepterer alle','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / TextIndividual Settings - Description'=>'Individuelle indstillinger - Beskrivelse','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / Text<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Legitimate-Interest">Legitimate Interest</translation-key> - Description'=>'<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Legitimate-Interest">Legitime interesser</translation-key> - beskrivelse','Frontend / Dialog / Link TextIndividual Privacy Preferences'=>'Individuelle privatlivsindstillinger','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / Text<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-More-Information">More Information</translation-key> - Description'=>'<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-More-Information">Flere oplysninger</translation-key> - Beskrivelse','Frontend / Dialog / Link TextPreferences'=>'Indstillinger','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / Text<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-No-Commitment">No Commitment</translation-key> - Description'=>'<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-No-Commitment">Ingen forpligtelse</translation-key> - Beskrivelse','Frontend / Dialog / Link TextSave Consent'=>'Gem samtykke','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / A11YThe following is a list of purposes of the IAB Transparency and Consent Framework (TCF) for which consent can be given. The TCF was created to help publishers, technology providers and advertisers comply with the EU GDPR and ePrivacy Directive.'=>'Følgende er en liste over formål med IAB Transparency and Consent Framework (TCF), som der kan gives samtykke til. TCF blev skabt for at hjælpe udgivere, teknologileverandører og annoncører med at overholde EU\'s GDPR og ePrivacy-direktiv.','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / Text<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Revoke">Revoke</translation-key> - Description'=>'<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Revoke">Tilbagekaldelse</translation-key> - Beskrivelse','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / A11YThe following is a list of service groups for which consent can be given. The first service group is essential and cannot be unchecked. These service groups are not part of the TCF standard.'=>'Følgende er en liste over servicegrupper, som der kan gives samtykke til. Den første servicegruppe er essentiel og kan ikke fravælges. Disse servicegrupper er ikke en del af TCF-standarden.','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / Text<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Technology">Technology</translation-key> - Description'=>'<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Technology">Teknologi</translation-key> - Beskrivelse','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / TextData Retention:'=>'Dataopbevaring:','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelTCF Consent History - Headline'=>'TCF-samtykkehistorik - Overskrift','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / TextDays'=>'Dage','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / HeadlineNon-TCF Standard Consent History - Headline'=>'Ikke-TCF standardsamtykkehistorik - Overskrift','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / TextPlease note that based on individual settings not all functions of the site may be available.'=>'Bemærk, at baseret på individuelle indstillinger er det ikke sikkert, at alle funktioner på hjemmesiden er tilgængelige.','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / HeadlineData Categories - Headline'=>'Datakategorier - Overskrift','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / TextSome of our <a href="#" role="button" data-borlabs-cookie-actions="vendors">{{ totalVendors }} partners</a> process your data (revocable at any time) based on <a href="#" role="button" data-borlabs-cookie-actions="leg-int">legitimate interest</a>.'=>'Nogle af vores <a href="#" role="button" data-borlabs-cookie-actions="vendors">{{ totalVendors }} partnere</a> behandler dine data (kan til enhver tid tilbagekaldes) baseret på <a href="#" role="button" data-borlabs-cookie-actions="leg-int">legitime interesser</a>.','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / TextYou can find more information about the use of your data and about our partners under <a href="#" role="button" data-borlabs-cookie-actions="preferences">Settings</a> or in our privacy policy.'=>'Du kan finde flere oplysninger om brugen af dine data og om vores partnere under <a href="#" role="button" data-borlabs-cookie-actions="preferences">Indstillinger</a> eller i vores privatlivspolitik.','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / HeadlineIllustrations - Headline'=>'Illustrationer - Overskrift','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / TextThere is no obligation to agree to the processing of your data in order to use this offer.'=>'Der er ingen forpligtelse til at acceptere behandlingen af dine data for at bruge dette tilbud.','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / HeadlineLegitimate Interests - Headline'=>'Legitime interesser - Overskrift','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / TextPersonal data can be processed (e.g. recognition features, IP addresses), for example for personalized ads and content or ad and content measurement.'=>'Personoplysninger kan behandles (f.eks. genkendelsesfunktioner, IP-adresser), f.eks. til personaliserede annoncer og indhold eller måling af annoncer og indhold.','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / HeadlineNon-TCF Standard Categories- Headline'=>'Ikke-TCF standardkategorier - Overskrift','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / TextWe cannot display certain contents without your consent. You can revoke or adjust your selection at any time under <a href="#" role="button" data-borlabs-cookie-actions="preferences">Settings</a>. Your selection will only be applied to this offer.'=>'Vi kan ikke vise bestemt indhold uden dit samtykke. Du kan til enhver tid tilbagekalde eller justere dit valg under <a href="#" role="button" data-borlabs-cookie-actions="preferences">Indstillinger</a>. Dit valg vil kun gælde for dette tilbud.','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / TextWe need your consent for us and our {{ totalVendors }} partners to use cookies and other technologies to deliver relevant content and advertising to you. This is how we finance and optimize our website.'=>'Vi har brug for dit samtykke til, at vi og vores {{ totalVendors }} partnere kan bruge cookies og andre teknologier til at levere relevant indhold og reklamer til dig. Det er sådan, vi finansierer og optimerer vores hjemmeside.','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / Consent HistoryTCF Vendors Consents'=>'Samtykker fra TCF-leverandører','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / Consent HistoryNon-TCF Standard Consents'=>'Ikke-TCF standardsamtykker','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / HeadlineStandard Data Retention - Headline'=>'Standarddataopbevaring - Overskrift','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / Consent HistoryData Categories'=>'Datakategorier','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / HeadlineVendor Information - Headline'=>'Oplysninger om leverandører - Overskrift','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / HeadlineFeatures'=>'Funktioner','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / HeadlineVendor Consent History - Headline'=>'Samtykkehistorik fra leverandører - Overskrift','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / HeadlineIllustrations'=>'Illustrationer','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / HeadlineNon-TCF Standard - Icon Label'=>'Ikke-TCF-standard - Ikonmærkat','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / HeadlineLegitimate Interests'=>'Legitime interesser','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / Link TextShow all Vendors - Button Text'=>'Vis alle leverandører - Knaptekst','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / HeadlineNon-TCF Standard Categories'=>'Ikke-TCF-standardkategorier','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / HeadlineCategories - Tab Title'=>'Kategorier - Fanetitel','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / HeadlinePurposes'=>'Formål','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / HeadlineLegitimate Interest - Tab Title'=>'Legitime interesser - Fanetitel','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / HeadlineSpecial Features'=>'Særlige funktioner','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / HeadlineVendors - Tab Title'=>'Leverandører - Fanetitel','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / HeadlineSpecial Purposes'=>'Særlige formål','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / Link TextVendor Legitimate Interest Claim - Link Text'=>'Leverandørs krav om legitime interesser - Linktekst','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / HeadlineStandard Data Retention'=>'Standarddataopbevaring','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / TextVendors - Plural'=>'Leverandører - Flertal','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / VendorsVendor Information'=>'Oplysninger om leverandører','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / Link TextVendor Privacy Policy - Link Text'=>'Leverandørens privatlivspolitik - Linktekst','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / VendorsHistory'=>'Historik','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / Placeholder Vendor Search - Placeholder'=>'Søg efter leverandører - Pladsholder','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / HeadlineNon-TCF Standard'=>'Ikke-TCF-standard','Backend / IAB TCF Cookie Box / TextVendors - Singular'=>'Leverandører - Singulær','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / ProviderShow all providers'=>'Vis alle udbydere','Backend / Dialog Localization / HeadlineImprint - Link Text'=>'Kontaktside - Linktekst','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / ProviderShow all vendors'=>'Vis alle leverandører','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelAge - Description'=>'Alder - Beskrivelse','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / HeadlineCategories'=>'Kategorier','Backend / Dialog Localization / Label<translation-key id="Individual-Settings">Individual Settings</translation-key> - Description'=>'<translation-key id="Individual-Settings">Individuelle indstillinger</translation-key> - Beskrivelse','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / HeadlineLegitimate Interest'=>'Legitime interesser','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelMore Information - Description'=>'Flere oplysninger - Beskrivelse','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / HeadlineVendors'=>'Leverandører','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelNo Obligation - Description'=>'Ingen forpligtelse - Beskrivelse','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / HeadlineLegitimate Interest Claim'=>'Krav om legitime interesser','Backend / Dialog Localization / Label<translation-key id="Non-EU-Data-Transfer">Non-EU Data Transfer</translation-key> - Description'=>'<translation-key id="Non-EU-Data-Transfer">Dataoverførsel uden for EU</translation-key> - Beskrivelse','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / ProviderVendors'=>'Leverandører','Backend / Dialog Localization / Label<translation-key id="Personal-Data">Personal Data</translation-key> - Description'=>'<translation-key id="Personal-Data">Personoplysninger</translation-key> - Beskrivelse','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / HeadlinePrivacy Policy'=>'Privatlivspolitik','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelRevoke - Description'=>'Tilbagekaldelse - Beskrivelse','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / ProviderSearch vendors...'=>'Søg efter leverandører ...','Backend / Dialog Localization / LabelTechnology - Description'=>'Teknologi - Beskrivelse','Frontend / IAB TCF Dialog / ProviderVendor'=>'Leverandør','Backend / Dialog Localization / HeadlinePrivacy - Link Text'=>'Databeskyttelse - Linktekst','Frontend / Dialog / Link TextImprint'=>'Kontaktside','Backend / Dialog Localization / HeadlineAdress'=>'Adresse','Frontend / Dialog / TextIf you are under 16 and wish to give consent to optional services, you must ask your legal guardians for permission.'=>'Hvis du er under 16 år og ønsker at give samtykke til valgfrie servicer, skal du bede dine værger om tilladelse.','Backend / Dialog Localization / HeadlineClose - Button Text'=>'Luk - Knaptekst','Frontend / Dialog / TextPlease note that based on individual settings not all functions of the site may be available.'=>'Bemærk, at baseret på individuelle indstillinger er det ikke sikkert, at alle funktioner på hjemmesiden er tilgængelige.','Backend / Dialog Localization / HeadlineCookie URL'=>'Cookie-URL','Frontend / Dialog / TextYou can find more information about the use of your data in our <a href="{{ privacyPageUrl }}">privacy policy</a>.'=>'Du kan finde flere oplysninger om brugen af dine data i vores <a href="{{ privacyPageUrl }}">privatlivspolitik</a>.','Backend / Dialog Localization / HeadlineDescription'=>'Beskrivelse','Frontend / Dialog / TextThere is no obligation to consent to the processing of your data in order to use this offer.'=>'Der er ingen forpligtelse til at samtykke til behandling af dine data for at bruge dette tilbud.','Frontend / Dialog / TextSome services process personal data in the USA. With your consent to use these services, you also consent to the processing of your data in the USA pursuant to Art. 49 (1) lit. a GDPR. The ECJ classifies the USA as a country with insufficient data protection according to EU standards. For example, there is a risk that U.S. authorities will process personal data in surveillance programs without any existing possibility of legal action for Europeans.'=>'Nogle servicer behandler personoplysninger i USA. Med dit samtykke til at bruge disse servicer giver du også samtykke til behandling af dine data i USA i henhold til art. 49 (1) lit. a GDPR. EU-Domstolen klassificerer USA som et land med utilstrækkelig databeskyttelse i henhold til EU-standarder. Der er f.eks. risiko for, at amerikanske myndigheder behandler personoplysninger i overvågningsprogrammer, uden at europæere har mulighed for at anlægge sag.','Frontend / Dialog / TextPersonal data may be processed (e.g. IP addresses), for example for personalized ads and content or ad and content measurement.'=>'Personoplysninger kan behandles (såsom IP-adresser), for eksempel til personaliserede annoncer og indhold eller måling af annoncer og indhold.','Frontend / Dialog / TextYou can revoke or adjust your selection at any time under <a href="#" role="button" data-borlabs-cookie-actions="preferences">Settings</a>.'=>'Du kan til enhver tid tilbagekalde eller justere dit valg under <a href="#" role="button" data-borlabs-cookie-actions="preferences">Indstillinger</a>.','Frontend / Dialog / TextWe use cookies and other technologies on our website. Some of them are essential, while others help us to improve this website and your experience.'=>'Vi bruger cookies og andre teknologier på vores hjemmeside. Nogle af dem er nødvendige, mens andre hjælper os med at forbedre denne hjemmeside og din oplevelse.','Frontend / Dialog / Link TextPrivacy Policy'=>'Privatlivspolitik','Frontend / Dialog / ProviderAddress'=>'Adresse','Frontend / Dialog / ProviderClose'=>'Luk','Frontend / Dialog / ProviderCookie URL'=>'Cookie-URL','Frontend / Dialog / ProviderDescription'=>'Beskrivelse','Frontend / Dialog / ProviderProvider Information'=>'Udbyderoplysninger','Frontend / Dialog / ProviderProvider Name'=>'Udbyderens navn','Frontend / Dialog / ProviderOpt-Out URL'=>'Opt-out-URL','Frontend / Dialog / ProviderPartners'=>'Partnere','Frontend / Dialog / ProviderProviders'=>'Udbydere','Frontend / Dialog / ProviderPrivacy Policy URL'=>'URL til privatlivspolitik','Frontend / Dialog / ProviderSearch providers...'=>'Søg efter udbydere ...','Frontend / Dialog / ProviderProvider'=>'Udbyder','Frontend / Dialog / Table HeadlineLifetime'=>'Levetid','Frontend / Dialog / Table HeadlinePurpose'=>'Formål','Frontend / Dialog / Table HeadlineFunctional'=>'Funktionel','Frontend / Dialog / Table HeadlineTracking'=>'Sporing','Frontend / Dialog / Table HeadlineType'=>'Type','Frontend / Dialog / Table HeadlineHTTP'=>'HTTP','Frontend / Dialog / Table HeadlineLocal Storage'=>'Lokal opbevaring','Frontend / Dialog / Table HeadlineSession Storage'=>'Sessionsopbevaring','Frontend / Dialog / Table HeadlineCookie(s)'=>'Cookie(s)','Frontend / Dialog / Table HeadlineDescription'=>'Beskrivelse','Frontend / Dialog / Table HeadlineHosts'=>'Værter','Frontend / Dialog / Table HeadlineName'=>'Navn','Frontend / Dialog / Table HeadlineData Collection'=>'Dataindsamling','Frontend / Dialog / Table HeadlineData Purpose'=>'Dataformål','Frontend / Dialog / Table HeadlineDistribution'=>'Distribution','Frontend / Dialog / Table HeadlineLegal Basis'=>'Juridisk grundlag','Frontend / Dialog / Table HeadlineTechnology'=>'Teknologi','Frontend / Dialog / Table HeadlineService Options'=>'Servicevalgmuligheder','Frontend / Dialog / HeadlineServices'=>'Servicer','Frontend / Dialog / ServicesSearch Services...'=>'Søg efter servicer','Frontend / Dialog / HeadlineService'=>'Service','Frontend / Dialog / URLhttps://borlabs.io/borlabs-cookie/'=>'https://borlabs.io/borlabs-cookie/','Frontend / Dialog / Consent HistoryUID'=>'UID','Seeder / Default Provider / DescriptionThis is a service that we cannot assign to any provider.'=>'Dette er en service, som vi ikke kan overdrage til nogen udbyder.','Seeder / Default Provider / NameUnknown'=>'Ukendt','Seeder / Default Provider / TextThis is the owner of this website. The owner is responsible for the content of this website and for the processing of your personal data.'=>'Dette er ejeren af denne hjemmeside. Ejeren er ansvarlig for indholdet af denne hjemmeside og for behandlingen af dine personoplysninger.','Seeder / Default Provider / NameOwner of this website'=>'Ejer af denne hjemmeside','Seeder / Default Service / DescriptionSaves the visitors preferences selected in the Dialog of Borlabs Cookie.'=>'Gemmer de besøgendes præferencer, der er valgt i Dialogboksen for Borlabs Cookie.','Seeder / Default Service / DescriptionBorlabs Cookie'=>'Borlabs Cookie','Seeder / Default Service / Cookie DescriptionThis cookie stores information regarding consent for service groups and individual services.'=>'Denne cookie gemmer oplysninger om samtykke til servicegrupper og individuelle servicer.','Seeder / Default Service / Cookie Description60 days'=>'60 dage','Seeder / Default Service Group / DescriptionEssential services enable basic functions and are necessary for the proper function of the website.'=>'Nødvendige servicer muliggør grundlæggende funktioner og er nødvendige for, at hjemmesiden kan fungere korrekt.','Seeder / Default Service Group / NameEssential'=>'Nødvendige','Seeder / Default Service Group / DescriptionContent from video platforms and social media platforms is blocked by default. If External Media services are accepted, access to those contents no longer requires manual consent.'=>'Indhold fra videoplatforme og sociale medieplatforme er blokeret som standard. Hvis eksterne medietjenester accepteres, kræver adgang til disse indhold ikke længere manuelt samtykke.','Seeder / Default Service Group / NameExternal Media'=>'Eksterne medier','Seeder / Default Service Group / DescriptionMarketing services are used by third-party advertisers or publishers to display personalized ads. They do this by tracking visitors across websites.'=>'Markedsføringsservicer bruges af tredjepartsannoncører eller udgivere til at vise personaliserede annoncer. Det gør de ved at spore besøgende på tværs af hjemmesider.','Seeder / Default Service Group / NameMarketing'=>'Markedsføring','Seeder / Default Service Group / DescriptionStatistics cookies collect usage information, enabling us to gain insights into how our visitors interact with our website.'=>'Statistikcookies indsamler oplysninger om brug, der giver os indsigt i, hvordan vores besøgende interagerer med vores hjemmeside.','Seeder / Default Service Group / NameStatistics'=>'Statistik','Frontend / Shortcode / Button TitleOpen Consent Preferences'=>'Åben samtykkeindstillinger','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelActive'=>'Aktiv','Backend / Dialog Appearance / Label<translation-key id="Backdrop">Backdrop</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Backdrop">Baggrund</translation-key>','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelBackground Color'=>'Baggrundsfarve','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelBorder Color'=>'Kantfarve','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelBorder Radius'=>'Kantradius','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelBottom'=>'Nederst','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelBottom Left'=>'Nederst venstre','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelBottom Right'=>'Nederst højre','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelButton'=>'Knap','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelButton Color'=>'Knapfarve','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelButton Text Color'=>'Knaptekstfarve','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelCard'=>'Kort','Backend / Global / TextCheckbox'=>'Afkrydsningsfelt','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelCSS'=>'CSS','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelDefault'=>'Standard','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelDialog'=>'Dialogboks','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelDialog Border Radius'=>'Kantradius på dialogboks','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelCard Border Radius'=>'Kantradius på kort','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelCard List Padding Medium Screen'=>'Padding på kortliste til medium skærm','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelCard List Padding Small Screen'=>'Padding på kortliste til lille skærm','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelAccept All - Button Color'=>'Acceptér alle - Knapfarve','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelAccept All - Button Text Color'=>'Acceptér alle - Knaptekstfarve','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelAccept Only Essential - Button Color'=>'Acceptér kun Nødvendige - Knapfarve','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelAccept Only Essential - Button Text Color'=>'Acceptér kun Nødvendige - Knaptekstfarve','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelClose - Button Color'=>'Luk - Knapfarve','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelClose - Button Text Color'=>'Luk - Knaptekstfarve','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelPrivacy Preferences - Button Color'=>'Privatlivsindstillinger - Knapfarve','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelPrivacy Preferences - Button Text Color'=>'Privatlivsindstillinger - Knaptekstfarve','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelSave Consent - Button Color'=>'Gem samtykke - Knapfarve','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelSave Consent - Button Text Color'=>'Gem samtykke - Knaptekstfarve','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelSelection - Button Color'=>'Valg - Knapfarve','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelSelection - Button Text Color'=>'Valg - Knaptekstfarve','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelCheck Mark'=>'Flueben','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelCheckbox Active'=>'Afkrydsningsfelt aktiv','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelCheckbox Border Radius'=>'Kantradius på afkrydsningsfelt','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelCheckbox Disabled'=>'Afkrydsningsfelt deaktiveret','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelCheckbox Inactive'=>'Afkrydsningsfelt inaktivt','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelControl Element'=>'Kontrolelement','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelDialog Footer'=>'Dialogboksens sidefod','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelList Border Radius'=>'Kantradius på liste','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelList Item Control Element'=>'Listeelementets kontrolelement','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelList Item Control Element Separator Color'=>'Listeelement kontrolelement separatorfarve','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelList Item Even'=>'Listeelement lige','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelList Item Odd'=>'Listeelement ulige','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelList Item Separator Color'=>'Separatorfarve for listelement','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelList Item Separator Width'=>'Separatorbredde for listeelement','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelList Padding Medium Screen'=>'Padding på liste til medium skærm','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelList Padding Small Screen'=>'Padding på liste til lille skærm','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelPrimary Link Color'=>'Primær linkfarve','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelSecondary Link Color'=>'Sekundær linkfarve','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelSearch Input'=>'Søgeinput','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelSearch Input Border Color'=>'Kantfarve på søgeinput','Backend / Cloud Scan / AlertToo many redirects'=>'For mange omdirigeringer','Backend / Content Blockers / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset all <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> settings. They will be reset to their default settings. Your custom <translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Content Blockers</translation-key> and the <translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Content Blockers</translation-key> installed via the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key> are not reset.'=>'Bekræft, at du ønsker at nulstille alle indstillinger for <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokker</translation-key>. De vil blive nulstillet til deres standardindstillinger. Dine tilpassede<translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Indholdsblokkere</translation-key> og de <translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Indholdsblokkere</translation-key>, der er installeret via <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Biblioteket</translation-key>, bliver ikke nulstillet.','Backend / Cloud Scan / AlertThe Borlabs Cloud API returned an error. Please check if Borlabs Cookie is up-to-date.'=>'Borlabs Cloud API returnerede en fejl. Tjek, om Borlabs Cookie er opdateret.','Backend / Content Blockers / Table HeadlineHost(s)'=>'Vært(er)','Backend / Cloud Scan / BreadcrumbCreate Scan'=>'Opret scanning','Backend / Content Blockers / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Cloud Scan / BreadcrumbScanner'=>'Scanner','Backend / Content Blockers / Table HeadlineName'=>'Navn','Backend / Cloud Scan / ButtonGo back'=>'Gå tilbage','Backend / Content Blockers / Table HeadlineStatus'=>'Status','Backend / Cloud Scan / Button<translation-key id="Button-Create-Scan">Create scan</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Button-Create-Scan">Opret scanning</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Symboler forklaret','Backend / Cloud Scan / FieldCustom scan URLs'=>'Tilpassede URL\'er til scanning','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Content Blockers</translation-key> section?'=>'Hvad er formålet med sektionen <translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Indholdsblokkere</translation-key>?','Backend / Cloud Scan / FieldEnable custom URL to scan'=>'Aktivér tilpasset URL til scanning','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextUsing <translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Content Blockers</translation-key>, you can automatically block iframes such as videos from <strong>YouTube</strong> or <translation-key id="oEmbeds">oEmbeds</translation-key> such as posts from <strong>Pinterest</strong>. Your visitor sees a message that a content has been blocked and has the possibility to reload this content by clicking on it. You can customize the text and design of the block message to suit your needs and theme.'=>'Med <translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Indholdsblokkere</translation-key> kan du automatisk blokere iframes, eksempelvis videoer fra <strong>YouTube</strong> eller <translation-key id="oEmbeds">oEmbeds</translation-key> som indlæg fra <strong>Pinterest</strong>. Din besøgende ser en besked om, at et indhold er blevet blokeret, og har mulighed for at genindlæse dette indhold ved at klikke på det. Du kan tilpasse teksten og designet af beskeden om blokering, så den passer til dine behov og dit tema.','Backend / Cloud Scan / FieldCustom page'=>'Tilpasset side','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextGeneral settings can be found under <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers">Blockers</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Content-Blockers">Content Blockers</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Content-Blockers-Settings">Settings</translation-key>.'=>'Generelle indstillinger findes under <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers">Blokkere</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Content-Blockers">Indholdsblokkere</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Content-Blockers-Settings">Indstillinger</translation-key>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / FieldPages to scan'=>'Sider, der skal scannes','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe visual appearance (colors, borders, etc.) can be customized under <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers">Blockers</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Content-Blockers">Content Blockers</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Content-Blockers-Appearance">Appearance</translation-key>.'=>'Det visuelle udseende (farver, rammer osv.) kan tilpasses under <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers">Blokkere</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Content-Blockers">Indholdsblokkere</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Blockers-Content-Blockers-Appearance">Udseende</translation-key>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / Field<translation-key id="Scan-type">Scan type</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Scan-type">Scanningstype</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> is active and does block content (iframes) of the configured hosts.'=>'<translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokker</translation-key> er aktiv og blokerer indhold (iframes) fra de konfigurerede værter.','Backend / Cloud Scan / HeadlineSelect pages to scan'=>'Vælg sider, der skal scannes','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextDelete the <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>. Not available for <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Content-Blocker-Default">Default</translation-key> or a <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> installed via the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key>.'=>'Slet <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokker</translation-key>. Ikke tilgængelig for <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokker</translation-key>: <translation-key id="Content-Blocker-Default">Indholdsblokkerstandard</translation-key> eller en <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokker</translation-key> installeret via <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Biblioteket</translation-key>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipPages to scan'=>'Sider, der skal scannes','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextEdit the <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'Redigér <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokker</translation-key>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipScan type'=>'Scanningstype','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> is inactive is and does not block content (iframes) of the configured hosts.'=>'<translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokker</translation-key> er inaktiv er og blokerer ikke indhold (iframes) fra de konfigurerede værter.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipIf you select this option, the expected scan will be about <strong>{{ numberOfSelectionOfSitesPerPostType }}</strong> pages.'=>'Hvis du vælger denne mulighed, vil den forventede scanning være på ca. <strong>{{ numberOfSelectionOfSitesPerPostType }}</strong> sider.','Backend / Content Blockers Settings / BreadcrumbContent Blocker - Settings'=>'Indholdsblokker - Indstillinger','Backend / Cloud Scan / Tip<translation-key id="Custom">Custom</translation-key>: Use this option to scan a specific page of your website.'=>'<translation-key id="Custom">Tilpasset</translation-key>: Brug denne mulighed til at scanne en bestemt side på din hjemmeside.','Backend / Content Blockers Settings / LabelHostname(s) Exclusion List'=>'Liste over udelukkede værtsnavne','Backend / Cloud Scan / Tip<translation-key id="Homepage">Homepage</translation-key>: Use this option to scan the homepage of your website.'=>'<translation-key id="Homepage">Hjemmeside</translation-key>: Brug denne mulighed til at scanne hjemmesiden på din hjemmeside.','Backend / Content Blockers Settings / LabelRemove Iframes and more in Feeds'=>'Fjern iframes og andet i feeds','Backend / Cloud Scan / Tip<translation-key id="Selection-Of-Sites-Per-Post-Type">Selection of sites per post type</translation-key>: Use this option to scan a selection of pages of your website. The scanner selects the homepage, the newest and the oldest page of each post type and its archive.'=>'<translation-key id="Selection-Of-Sites-Per-Post-Type">Udvælgelse af sider pr. indlægsstype</translation-key>: Brug denne mulighed til at scanne et udvalg af sider på din hjemmeside. Scanneren vælger startsiden, den nyeste og den ældste side for hvert indlægstype og dens arkiv.','Backend / Content Blockers Settings / Label<translation-key id="Virtual-Hostnames-Exclusion-List">Virtual Hostnames Exclusion List</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Virtual-Hostnames-Exclusion-List">Liste over udelukkede virtuelle værtsnavne</translation-key>','Backend / Cloud Scan / Tip<translation-key id="Audit">Audit</translation-key>: Use this scan type to verify that your website does not load cookies or external resources without obtaining the appropriate consent.'=>'<translation-key id="Audit">Audit</translation-key>: Brug denne scanningstype til at kontrollere, at din hjemmeside ikke indlæser cookies eller eksterne ressourcer uden at indhente det nødvendige samtykke.','Backend / Content Blockers Settings / HeadlineGeneral Settings'=>'Generelle indstillinger','Backend / Cloud Scan / Tip<translation-key id="Setup">Setup</translation-key>: Use this scan type to determine which cookies or external resources are used by your website. After the scan, you will receive recommendations for packages that you can install to block these cookies or external resources.'=>'<translation-key id="Setup">Opsætning</translation-key>: Brug denne scanningstype til at finde ud af, hvilke cookies eller eksterne ressourcer der bruges af din hjemmeside. Efter scanningen vil du modtage anbefalinger til pakker, som du kan installere for at blokere disse cookies eller eksterne ressourcer.','Backend / Content Blockers Settings / HeadlineReset Content Blocker Settings'=>'Nulstil indstillinger for indholdsblokkere','Backend / Cloud Scan / AlertWe have no additional suggestions.'=>'Vi har ingen yderligere forslag.','Backend / Content Blockers Settings / HintOne <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key> per line. When a <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key> is recognized (for example within the src-attribute of an iframe) the content will not be blocked.'=>'Ét <translation-key id="Hostname">Værtsnavn</translation-key> per linje. Når et <translation-key id="Hostname">Værtsnavn</translation-key> genkendes (f.eks. i src-attributten i en iframe), blokeres indholdet ikke.','Backend / Cloud Scan / AlertNo external resource found.'=>'Ingen ekstern ressource fundet.','Backend / Content Blockers Settings / HintRemoves iframes, blocked content and all output of the <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcodes</translation-key> of <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> in feeds. Due technical limitations it is not possible to provide the click-to-load functionality in feeds.'=>'Fjerner iframes, blokeret indhold og al uddata fra <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>s <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcodes</translation-key> i feeds. På grund af tekniske begrænsninger er det ikke muligt at levere funktionen click-to-load i feeds.','Backend / Cloud Scan / AlertWe found no suggestions.'=>'Vi fandt ingen forslag.','Backend / Content Blockers Settings / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset all <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> settings. They will be reset to their default settings.'=>'Bekræft, at du vil nulstille alle indstillinger for <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokker</translation-key>. De vil blive nulstillet til deres standardindstillinger.','Backend / Cloud Scan / BreadcrumbScanning'=>'Scanning','Backend / Cloud Scan / BreadcrumbScan results'=>'Scanningsresultater','Backend / Content Blockers Settings / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is a <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key>?'=>'Hvad er et <translation-key id="Hostname">Værtsnavn</translation-key>?','Backend / Cloud Scan / FieldCloud Scan ID'=>'Cloudscan-id','Backend / Content Blockers Settings / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key> is the domain name of the website. For example, if the URL of the website is <strong><em>https://www.example.com</em></strong>, the <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key> is <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong>.'=>'<translation-key id="Hostname">Værtsnavnet</translation-key> er hjemmesidens domænenavn. Hvis hjemmesidens URL f.eks. er <strong><em>https://www.example.com</em></strong>, så er <translation-key id="Hostname">Værtsnavn</translation-key> <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / FieldCreated at'=>'Oprettet på','Backend / Dashboard / Alert MessageNo data available yet. Please try again in a few hours.'=>'Ingen data tilgængelige endnu. Prøv igen om et par timer.','Backend / Cloud Scan / FieldType'=>'Type','Backend / Dashboard / BreadcrumbDashboard'=>'Kontrolpanel','Backend / Cloud Scan / FieldURLs'=>'URL\'er','Backend / Dashboard / Button Title7 Days'=>'7 dage','Backend / Cloud Scan / HeadlineCookies'=>'Cookies','Backend / Dashboard / Button Title30 Days'=>'30 dage','Backend / Cloud Scan / HeadlineExternal resources'=>'Eksterne ressourcer','Backend / Dashboard / Button TitleToday'=>'I dag','Backend / Cloud Scan / HeadlineScanned pages'=>'Scannede sider','Backend / Dashboard / Button Title30 Days by Service'=>'30 dage efter service','Backend / Cloud Scan / HeadlineScan results'=>'Scanningsresultater','Backend / Cloud Scan / HeadlineSuggested Packages Already Installed'=>'Foreslåede pakker, der allerede er installeret','Backend / Cloud Scan / HeadlineSuggested Packages to Install'=>'Foreslåede pakker at installere','Backend / Cloud Scan / HeadlineSuggestions'=>'Forslag','Backend / Cloud Scan / Table<translation-key id="External-hostname">External hostname</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="External-hostname">Eksternt værtsnavn</translation-key>','Backend / Cloud Scan / Table<translation-key id="Failure-type">Failure type</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Failure-type">Fejltype</translation-key>','Backend / Dashboard / HeadlineAcknowledgement'=>'Anerkendelse','Backend / Cloud Scan / TableHostname'=>'Værtsnavn','Backend / Dashboard / HeadlineContributors'=>'Bidragydere','Backend / Cloud Scan / TableLifetime'=>'Levetid','Backend / Dashboard / Headline<span>Statistics</span> <small>-</small> <small>Cookie Version {{ cookieVersion }}</small>'=>'<span>Statistik</span> <small>-</small> <small>Cookie version {{ cookieVersion }}</small>','Backend / Cloud Scan / TableName'=>'Navn','Backend / Cloud Scan / Table<translation-key id="Number-of-resources">Number of resources</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Number-of-resources">Antal ressourcer</translation-key>','Backend / Dashboard / HeadlineNews'=>'Nyheder','Backend / Cloud Scan / TableFound on page'=>'Fundet på side','Backend / Cloud Scan / TablePath'=>'Sti','Backend / Cloud Scan / TableResource URL'=>'Ressource-URL','Backend / Dashboard / TextDevelopment &amp; Infrastructure'=>'Udvikling og infrastruktur','Backend / Cloud Scan / TableStatus'=>'Status','Backend / Dashboard / TextFurther Contributors'=>'Yderligere bidragydere','Backend / Cloud Scan / TableSuggested package'=>'Foreslået pakke','Backend / Dashboard / Texthere'=>'her','Backend / Cloud Scan / TableURL'=>'URL','Backend / Dashboard / TextIn memory of Sergii Kovalenko.'=>'Til minde om Sergii Kovalenko.','Backend / Cloud Scan / Textdays'=>'dage','Backend / Cloud Scan / TextFailed'=>'Mislykket','Backend / Dashboard / TextFor more information about what data we collect and for what purpose, <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="%s" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span>click here</span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>.'=>'For flere oplysninger om, hvilke data vi har brug for og til hvilket formål, <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="%s" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span>klik her</span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TextSuccess'=>'Succes','Backend / Cloud Scan / TextScan in progress'=>'Scanning i gang','Backend / Cloud Scan / TextScan is analysing'=>'Scanning analyserer','Backend / Cloud Scan / TextScanning'=>'Scanning','Backend / Cloud Scan / TextSession'=>'Session','Backend / Cloud Scan / AlertThe scanner\'s analysis can make suggestions for installing packages that prevent the inclusion of external resources or improve compatibility between the theme and installed plugins.'=>'Scannerens analyse kan komme med forslag til installation af pakker, der forhindrer inkludering af eksterne ressourcer eller forbedrer kompatibiliteten mellem temaet og installerede plugins.','Backend / Cloud Scan / AlertClick on the <translation-key id="Button-Details">Details</translation-key> button to get more information about the package. Once the package is installed, you will be redirected back to this page to proceed with the installation of the next package.'=>'Klik på knappen <translation-key id="Button-Details">Knapoplysninger</translation-key> for at få mere information om pakken. Når pakken er installeret, vil du blive omdirigeret tilbage til denne side for at fortsætte med installationen af den næste pakke.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipTo comply with data protection, cookies must be blocked in most cases until consent is given. Only essential cookies may be set without consent. An essential cookie could be one that, for instance, stores the shopping cart contents or the selected language.'=>'På grund af databeskyttelse skal cookies i de fleste tilfælde blokeres, indtil der er givet samtykke. Kun nødvendige cookies må sættes uden samtykke. En nødvendig cookie kan f.eks. være en, der gemmer indholdet af indkøbskurven eller det valgte sprog.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipClick the icon to view sample locations associated with the detected cookie.'=>'Klik på ikonet for at se eksempler på adresser, der er forbundet med den registrerede cookie.','Backend / Cloud Scan / Tip<translation-key id="Suggested-package">Suggested package</translation-key>: This column lists a recommended package to install to block the cookie if the cookie is not essential.'=>'<translation-key id="Suggested-package">Foreslået pakke</translation-key>: Denne kolonne viser en anbefalet pakke, der skal installeres for at blokere cookien, hvis den ikke er essentiel.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipCookies'=>'Cookies','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipExternal resources'=>'Eksterne ressourcer','Backend / Dashboard / URLhttps://borlabs.io/borlabs-cookie/telemetry/'=>'https://borlabs.io/borlabs-cookie/telemetry/','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipStatus'=>'Status','Backend / Dashboard / URLhttps://borlabs.io/support/?utm_source=Borlabs+Cookie&utm_medium=Dashboard+Link&utm_campaign=Analysis'=>'https://borlabs.io/support/?utm_source=Borlabs+Cookie&utm_medium=Dashboard+Link&utm_campaign=Analysis','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipExternal resources are resources that are loaded from a different domain than the page itself. For example, if you have a page with the URL <strong><em>https://www.example.com</em></strong> and this page loads a resource from <strong><em>https://www.example.org</em></strong>, then this resource is considered an external resource. To comply with data protection, in most cases, these external resources must be blocked until consent is given.'=>'Eksterne ressourcer er ressourcer, der indlæses fra et andet domæne end selve siden. Hvis du f.eks. har en side med URL\'en <strong><em>https://www.example.com</em></strong> og denne side indlæser en ressource fra <strong><em>https://www.example.org</em></strong>så betragtes denne ressource som en ekstern ressource. For at overholde databeskyttelsen skal disse eksterne ressourcer i de fleste tilfælde blokeres, indtil der er givet samtykke.','Seeder / Default Content Blocker / DescriptionThe <strong><em>Default</em> Content Blocker</strong> is a special type that is always used when no specific <strong>Content Blocker</strong> was found.<br>Therefore it is not possible to use the <strong>Unblock all</strong> feature.'=>'Den <strong><em>standardmæssige</em> Indholdsblokker</strong>er en særlig type, der altid bruges, når der ikke blev fundet nogen specifik <strong>Indholdsblokker</strong>.<br>Derfor er det ikke muligt at bruge funktionen <strong>Fjern blokering af alle</strong>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipClick on the icon to get detailed information about the external resource. In the details you can find examples of discovered resources and their respective locations.'=>'Klik på ikonet for at få detaljerede oplysninger om den eksterne ressource. I detaljerne kan du finde eksempler på fundne ressourcer og deres respektive adresser.','Backend / Cloud Scan / Tip<translation-key id="External-hostname">External hostname</translation-key>: Resources are being loaded from this source.'=>'<translation-key id="External-hostname">Eksternt værtsnavn</translation-key>: Ressourcer indlæses fra denne kilde.','Backend / Cloud Scan / Tip<translation-key id="Number-of-resources">Number of resources</translation-key>: The number of resources loaded from this source. The resources found are limited to 10 per hostname.'=>'<translation-key id="Number-of-resources">Antal ressourcer</translation-key>: Antallet af ressourcer, der er indlæst fra denne kilde. De fundne ressourcer er begrænset til 10 per værtsnavn.','Backend / Cloud Scan / Tip<translation-key id="Suggested-package">Suggested package</translation-key>: This column lists a recommended package to install to block the external resource.'=>'<translation-key id="Suggested-package">Foreslået pakke</translation-key>: Denne kolonne viser en anbefalet pakke, der skal installeres for at blokere den eksterne ressource.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipFailed: The scanner could not scan the page. More information can be found in the <translation-key id="Failure-type">Failure type</translation-key> column.'=>'Mislykket: Scanneren kunne ikke scanne siden. Flere oplysninger kan findes i kolonnen <translation-key id="Failure-type">Fejltype</translation-key>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipSuccess: The page was scanned successfully.'=>'Succes: Siden blev succesfuldt scannet.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipScanning: The page is being scanned.'=>'Scanning: Siden er ved at blive scannet.','Backend / Cloud Scan / AlertNo <translation-key id="Scans">Scans</translation-key> configured.'=>'Ingen <translation-key id="Scans">Scanninger</translation-key> er konfigureret.','Backend / Cloud Scan / HeadlineScanner'=>'Scanner','Backend / Cloud Scan / TableCloud Scan ID'=>'Cloudscan-id','Backend / Cloud Scan / TableCreated at'=>'Oprettet den','Backend / Cloud Scan / TableScanned pages'=>'Scannede sider','Backend / Cloud Scan / TableType'=>'Type','Backend / Cloud Scan / Things to know / TextThe scanner will help you set up <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> that will help you make your website privacy compliant. Two scan options are available for this purpose.'=>'Scanneren hjælper dig med at opsætte <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>, der hjælper dig med at gøre din hjemmeside i overensstemmelse med privatlivsreglerne. Der er to scanningsmuligheder til rådighed til dette formål.','Backend / Cloud Scan / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the functionality of the scanner?'=>'Hvad er scannerens funktionalitet?','Backend / Compatibility Patch Details / Alert MessageError: The required file is missing. To resolve this issue, please reinstall the package.'=>'Fejl: Den påkrævede fil mangler. Geninstallér pakken for at løse problemet.','Backend  / Compatibility Patch Details /  Description ListCalculated Hash'=>'Beregnet hash','Backend  / Compatibility Patch Details /  Description ListFile Name'=>'Filnavn','Backend  / Compatibility Patch Details /  Description ListFile Path'=>'Filsti','Backend  / Compatibility Patch Details /  Description ListID'=>'ID','Backend  / Compatibility Patch Details /  Description ListInstalled at'=>'Installeret den','Backend  / Compatibility Patch Details /  Description ListPackage'=>'Pakke','Backend  / Compatibility Patch Details /  Description ListRequired Hash'=>'Påkrævet hash','Backend  / Compatibility Patch Details /  Description ListUpdated at'=>'Opdateret den','Backend  / Compatibility Patch Details /  Description ListValid'=>'Gyldig','Backend  / Compatibility Patch Details /  Description ListVersion'=>'Version','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patch">Compatibility Patch</translation-key> configured.'=>'Ingen <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patch">Kompatibilitetsrettelse</translation-key> konfigureret.','Backend / Compatibility Patches / BreadcrumbCompatibility Patches'=>'Kompatibilitetsrettelser','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Headline<translation-key id="Compatibility-Patches">Compatibility Patches</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Compatibility-Patches">Kompatibilitetsrettelser</translation-key>','Backend / Compatibility Patches / PlaceholderSearch key or file name...'=>'Søg efter nøgle eller filnavn ...','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Table HeadlinePackage'=>'Pakke','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Table HeadlineFile name'=>'Filens navn','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Table HeadlineHash'=>'Hash','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Table HeadlineValid'=>'Gyldig','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Things to knowClick on the icon to get detailed information about the <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patch">Compatibility Patch</translation-key>.'=>'Klik på ikonet for at få detaljerede oplysninger om <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patch">Kompatibilitetsrettelsen</translation-key>.','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patches">Compatibility Patches</translation-key> section?'=>'Hvad er formålet med sektionen <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patches">Kompatibilitetsrettelser</translation-key>?','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Symboler forklaret','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Things to knowThe file of the <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patch">Compatibility Patch</translation-key> is invalid. Please reinstall the package via the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key> to resolve this issue.'=>'Filen til <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patch">Kompatibilitetsrettelsen</translation-key> er ugyldig. Geninstallér pakken via <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Biblioteket</translation-key> for at løse dette problem.','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Things to knowIn this section, you can see all <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patches">Compatibility Patches</translation-key> that have been installed by packages from the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key>.'=>'I denne sektion kan du se alle <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patches">Kompatibilitetsrettelser</translation-key>, der er blevet installeret af pakker fra <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Biblioteket</translation-key>.','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Things to knowA <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patch">Compatibility Patch</translation-key> is used to enhance compatibility with other <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Themes">Themes</translation-key> external services.'=>'En <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patch">Kompatibilitetsrettelse</translation-key> bruges til at forbedre kompatibiliteten med andre <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Themes">Temaer</translation-key> og eksterne servicer.','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Things to knowThe file of the <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patch">Compatibility Patch</translation-key> is valid.'=>'Filen med <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patch">Kompatibilitetsrettelsen</translation-key> er gyldig.','Backend / Consent Log / Alert MessageThe <translation-key id="Consent-Log">Consent Log</translation-key> could not be found.'=>'<translation-key id="Consent-Log">Samtykkelogfil</translation-key>gen kunne ikke findes.','Backend / Consent Log / Breadcrumb<translation-key id="Consent-Logs">Consent Logs</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Consent-Logs">Samtykkelogfiler</translation-key>','Backend / Consent Log / BreadcrumbDetails'=>'Oplysninger','Backend / Consent Log / FieldConsents'=>'Samtykker','Backend / Consent Log / FieldCookie Version'=>'Cookieversion','Backend / Consent Log / LabelIAB TCF TC String'=>'IAB TCF TC-streng','Backend / Consent Log / LabelIs Latest Consent'=>'Er seneste samtykke','Backend / Consent Log / LabelUID'=>'UID','Backend / Consent Log / HintA version number is assigned to the cookie of <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. It is used to ask the visitor for consent again when changes are made to the cookies. If the version number in the cookie differs from the current version number, the consent dialog appears to the visitor.'=>'Et versionsnummer er tildelt cookien fra <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> Cookie. Det bruges til at bede den besøgende om samtykke igen, når der foretages ændringer i cookies. Hvis versionsnummeret i cookien adskiller sig fra det aktuelle versionsnummer, vises samtykkedialogboksen for den besøgende.','Backend / Consent Log / HintThe <translation-key id="TC-String">TC String</translation-key> is an encoded depiction of user consent choices, generated through interactions with <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. It informs publishers, advertisers, and ad tech vendors of the permitted uses of user data, based on users\' consent decisions.'=>'<translation-key id="TC-String">TC-streng</translation-key> er en kodet skildring af brugernes samtykkevalg, genereret gennem interaktioner med <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. Den informerer udgivere, annoncører og leverandører af annonceteknologi om de tilladte anvendelser af brugerdata, baseret på brugernes beslutninger om samtykke.','Backend / Consent Log / HintThe <translation-key id="UID">UID</translation-key> is a unique identifier of the user, generated through interactions with <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.'=>'<translation-key id="UID">UID</translation-key> er en unik identifikation af brugeren, genereret gennem interaktioner med <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.','Backend / Consent Log / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Consent-Logs">Consent Logs</translation-key> stored.'=>'Ingen <translation-key id="Consent-Logs">Samtykkelogfiler</translation-key> gemt.','Backend / Consent Log / Headline<translation-key id="Consent-Logs">Consent Logs</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Consent-Logs">Samtykkelogfiler</translation-key>','Backend / Consent Log / PlaceholderSearch UID...'=>'Søg efter UID ...','Backend / Consent Log / Table HeadlineCookie Version'=>'Cookieversion','Backend / Consent Log / Table Headline<translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Consent">IAB TCF Consent</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Consent">IAB TCF-samtykke</translation-key>','Backend / Consent Log / Table HeadlineService Consents'=>'Servicesamtykker','Backend / Consent Log / Table HeadlineStamp'=>'Dato- og tidsstempel','Backend / Consent Log / Table HeadlineUID'=>'UID','Backend / Consent Log / Things to know / HeadlineClick on the icon to view details of the user\'s consents.'=>'Klik på ikonet for at se detaljer om brugerens samtykker.','Backend / Consent Log / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Consent-Logs">Consent Logs</translation-key> show you the history of the user\'s consents. You can see which services the user has consented to and which not.'=>'<translation-key id="Consent-Logs">Samtykkelogfilerne</translation-key> viser dig historikken for brugerens samtykker. Du kan se, hvilke servicer brugeren har samtykket til, og hvilke brugerne ikke har.','Backend / Consent Log / Things to know / TextDue to the volume of consent logs that can be accumulated, only consent logs from the past 7 days are displayed here. However, you can access older log entries by inputting the UID into the search field.'=>'På grund af mængden af samtykkelogfiler, der kan akkumuleres, vises kun samtykkelogfiler fra de sidste syv dage her. Du kan dog få adgang til ældre logposter ved at indtaste UID\'et i søgefeltet.','Backend / Consent Log / Things to know / HeadlineWhat are Consent Logs?'=>'Hvad er samtykkelogfiler?','Backend / Consent Log / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Symboler forklaret','Backend / Consent Log / Things to know / Text<translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Consent">IAB TCF Consent</translation-key>: The last consent has granted consent to the <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Vendors">Vendors</translation-key> of the IAB TCF.'=>'<translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Consent">IAB TCF-samtykke</translation-key>: Den sidste tilladelse har givet samtykke til <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Vendors">Leverandørerne</translation-key> af IAB TCF.','Backend / Consent Log / Things to know / Text<translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Consent">IAB TCF Consent</translation-key>: The last consent did not granted consent to the <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Vendors">Vendors</translation-key> of the IAB TCF.'=>'<translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Consent">IAB TCF-samtykke</translation-key>: Den sidste tilladelse gav ikke samtykke til <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Vendors">Leverandørerne</translation-key> af IAB TCF.','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / BreadcrumbContent Blocker - Appearance'=>'Indholdsblokker - Udseende','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / Label<translation-key id="Background-Color">Background Color</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Background-Color">Baggrundsfarve</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelBorder Radius'=>'Kantradius','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelBottom Left'=>'Nederst venstre','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelBottom Right'=>'Nederst højre','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelButton'=>'Knap','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelButton Border Radius'=>'Kantradius på knap','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelButton Color'=>'Knapfarve','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelButton Text Color'=>'Knaptekstfarve','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelContent Blocker'=>'Indholdsblokker','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelDefault'=>'Standard','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelFont Family'=>'Skriftfamilie','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelHover'=>'Hover','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelLink Color'=>'Linkfarve','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelOpacity'=>'Opacitet','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelSeparator Color'=>'Separatorfarve','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelSeparator Width'=>'Separatorbredde','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelText Color'=>'Tekstfarve','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelTop Left'=>'Øverst venstre','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelTop Right'=>'Øverst højre','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / HeadlineAppearance Settings'=>'Indstillinger for udseende','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / HeadlineReset Content Blocker Settings'=>'Indstillinger for nulstilling af indholdsblokker','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / HintDefines the visibility of the <translation-key id="Background-Color">Background Color</translation-key>.'=>'Angiver synligheden af <translation-key id="Background-Color">Baggrundsfarve</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / HintChoose which font you want to use. Your themes font is the default setting.'=>'Vælg, hvilken skrifttype du vil bruge. Dit temas skrifttype er standardindstillingen.','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / HintBased on the base font size, the font size of all elements are automatically adjusted proportionally.'=>'Baseret på standardskriftstørrelsen justeres skriftstørrelsen på alle elementer automatisk proportionalt.','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset all <translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Content Blockers</translation-key> settings. They will be reset to their default settings.'=>'Bekræft, at du vil nulstille alle indstillinger for <translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Indholdsblokkere</translation-key>. De vil blive nulstillet til deres standardindstillinger.','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / Input PlaceholderEnter custom font family'=>'Indtast tilpasset skriftfamilie','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> Individual Settings'=>'Individuelle indstillinger for <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokker</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / Things to know / TextPlease note that the settings for <translation-key id="Button-Radius">Button Radius</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Button-Color">Button Color</translation-key>, and <translation-key id="Button-Text-Color">Button Text Color</translation-key> are often overwritten with the individual settings of a <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'Bemærk, at indstillingerne for <translation-key id="Button-Radius">Knapradius</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Button-Color">Knapfarve</translation-key> og <translation-key id="Button-Text-Color">Knaptekstfarve</translation-key> ofte overskrives af de individuelle indstillinger for en <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokker</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Alert MessageThe selected <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> is not available in the current language.'=>'Den valgte <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokker</translation-key> er ikke tilgængelig på det aktuelle sprog.','Backend / Content Blockers / Alert MessageThe selected <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> does not match the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> of the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Den valgte <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyder</translation-key> matcher ikke <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyderen</translation-key> af <translation-key id="Service">Servicen</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Alert MessageThe selected <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> is not available in the current language.'=>'Den valgte <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyder</translation-key> er ikke tilgængelig på det aktuelle sprog.','Backend / Content Blockers / Alert MessageThe selected <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> does not exist.'=>'Den valgte <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyder</translation-key> findes ikke.','Backend / Content Blockers / Alert MessageThe selected <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> does not exist.'=>'Den valgte <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> findes ikke.','Backend / Content Blockers / Alert MessageThe selected <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is not available in the current language.'=>'Den valgte <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> er ikke tilgængelig på det aktuelle sprog.','Backend / Content Blockers / BreadcrumbEdit: {{ name }}'=>'Redigér: {{ name }}','Backend / Content Blockers / BreadcrumbContent Blockers'=>'Indholdsblokkere','Backend / Content Blockers / BreadcrumbNew'=>'Ny','Backend / Content Blockers / Button TitleApply Preset'=>'Anvend skabelon','Backend / Content Blockers / Button TitleSelect or Upload Image'=>'Vælg eller upload billede','Backend / Content Blockers / Button TitleUse this media'=>'Brug dette medie','Backend / Content Blockers / LabelHost(s)'=>'Vært(er)','Backend / Content Blockers / Label<translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blockers / LabelID'=>'ID','Backend / Content Blockers / LabelName'=>'Navn','Backend / Content Blockers / LabelPreset'=>'Skabelon','Backend / Content Blockers / Label<translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-HTML">HTML</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-HTML">HTML</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blockers / Label<translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-Image">Image</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-Image">Billede</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blockers / LabelProvider List'=>'Liste over udbydere','Backend / Content Blockers / LabelService'=>'Service','Backend / Content Blockers / Label<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blockers / LabelStatus'=>'Status','Backend / Content Blockers / HeadlineContent Blocker Information'=>'Oplysninger om indholdsblokker','Backend / Content Blockers / HeadlineContent Blocker Settings'=>'Indstillinger for indholdsblokker','Backend / Content Blockers / HeadlineJavaScript'=>'JavaScript','Backend / Content Blockers / Headline<translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content">Preview Blocked Content</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content">Forhåndsvisning af blokeret indhold</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blockers / HeadlineProvider Information'=>'Udbyderoplysninger','Backend / Content Blockers / HeadlineService Information'=>'Serviceoplysninger','Backend / Content Blockers / HintOnly use JavaScript, do not use <strong><em>&lt;script&gt;</em></strong> tags!'=>'Brug kun JavaScript, brug ikke <strong><em>&lt;script&gt;</em></strong> tags!','Backend / Content Blockers / Hint<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be set. The <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be at least 3 characters long and may only contain: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>'=>'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> skal være indstillet. <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key>\'et skal være mindst tre tegn langt og må kun indeholde: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>','Backend / Content Blockers / HintThe name of the <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> which can be used within the <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content">Preview Blocked Content</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-HTML">HTML</translation-key> code by using the variable <strong><em>{{ name }}</em></strong>.'=>'Navnet på <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokkeren</translation-key>, som kan bruges i <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content">Forhåndsvisning af blokeret indhold</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-HTML">HTML</translation-key>-koden ved hjælp af variablen <strong><em>{{ name }}</em></strong>.','Backend / Content Blockers / HintThis CSS will be used for the preview of the blocked content.'=>'Denne CSS vil blive brugt til forhåndsvisning af det blokerede indhold.','Backend / Content Blockers / HintThis HTML will be used as the preview of the blocked content. You can use the following variables within the HTML code: <strong><em>{{ name }}</em></strong> to place the name of the <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> and <strong><em>{{ previewImage }}</em></strong> to place the URL of the <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-Image">Image</translation-key>.'=>'Denne HTML vil blive brugt som forhåndsvisning af det blokerede indhold. Du kan bruge følgende variabler i HTML-koden: <strong><em>{{ name }}</em></strong> til at placere navnet på <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokkeren</translation-key> og <strong><em>{{ previewImage }}</em></strong> til at placere <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-Image">Billede</translation-key>ts URL.','Backend / Content Blockers / HintThis image is used as a preview for the blocked content (only with <translation-key id="Preset-B">Preset B</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Preset-C">Preset C</translation-key>). The URL of the image can be accessed within the <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content">Preview Blocked Content</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-HTML">HTML</translation-key> with the <strong><em>{{ previewImage }}</em></strong> variable.'=>'Dette billede bruges som en forhåndsvisning af det blokerede indhold (kun med <translation-key id="Preset-B">Skabelon B</translation-key> og <translation-key id="Preset-C">Skabelon C</translation-key>). Billedets URL kan tilgås i <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content">Forhåndsvisning af blokeret indhold</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-HTML">HTML</translation-key> med <strong><em>{{ previewImage }}</em></strong> variabel.','Backend / Content Blockers / HintUse this <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> if automatic detection does not work.'=>'Brug denne <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key>, hvis den automatiske registrering ikke virker.','Backend / Content Blockers / HintThe status of this <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>. If enabled it does block content (iframes) of the configured <translation-key id="Locations">Locations</translation-key>.'=>'Status for denne <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokker</translation-key>. Hvis den er aktiveret, blokerer den indhold (iframes) på de konfigurerede <translation-key id="Locations">Adresser</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / OptionNo Service'=>'Ingen service','Backend / Content Blockers / OptionPreset A - Default'=>'Skabelon A - Standard','Backend / Content Blockers / Option<translation-key id="Preset-B">Preset B</translation-key> - Default + Background Image'=>'<translation-key id="Preset-B">Skabelon B</translation-key> - Standard + Baggrundsbillede','Backend / Content Blockers / Option<translation-key id="Preset-C">Preset C</translation-key> - Video Player'=>'<translation-key id="Preset-C">Skabelon C</translation-key> - Videoafspiller','Backend / Content Blockers / Input Placeholder...block this...'=>'... blokér dette ...','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe code is executed in a function that uses the variable <strong><em>el</em></strong> as a parameter. <strong><em>el</em></strong> contains the unlocked object.'=>'Koden udføres i en funktion, der bruger variablen <strong><em>el</em></strong> som parameter. <strong><em>el</em></strong> indeholder det oplåste objekt.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / Code Examplefunction (contentBlockerData, el) { /* Here is your initialization code */ }'=>'function (contentBlockerData, el) { /* Her er din initialiseringskode */ }','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineFor Developers'=>'For udviklere','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineGlobal JavaScript'=>'Global JavaScript','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineInitialization JavaScript'=>'Initialisering af JavaScript','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> information?'=>'Hvad er formålet med oplysninger om <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyder</translation-key>?','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> information?'=>'Hvad er formålet med <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>?','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> explained'=>'<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> forklaret','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextJavaScript stored in the <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> field is executed once a blocked content is unblocked by the visitor (meaning only once per page). Use this, for example, to load an external JavaScript library.'=>'JavaScript, der er opbevaret i feltet <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key>, udføres, når blokeringen af blokeret indhold fjernes af den besøgende (dvs. kun én gang pr. side). Brug det f.eks. til at indlæse et eksternt JavaScript-bibliotek.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextTo execute the JavaScript stored in the <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> field before the blocked content is loaded, activate the option <translation-key id="Execute-Global-code-before-unblocking">Execute Global code before unblocking</translation-key>.'=>'Hvis du vil udføre det JavaScript, der er gemt i feltet <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key>, før det blokerede indhold indlæses, skal du aktivere indstillingen <translation-key id="Execute-Global-code-before-unblocking">Udfør global kode før fjerner blokering</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextIf this option is enabled and a visitor unblocks the content, the JavaScript from the <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> field will be executed before the blocked content is loaded.'=>'Hvis denne indstilling er aktiveret, og en besøgende fjerner blokeringen af indholdet, vil JavaScript fra feltet <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> blive udført, før det blokerede indhold indlæses.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / Code Examplefunction (contentBlockerData) { /* Here is your global code */ }'=>'function (contentBlockerData) { /* Her er din globale kode */ }','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextJavaScript stored in the <translation-key id="Initialization">Initialization</translation-key> field is executed with every unblock of blocked content (meaning as many times as the visitor unblocks content). It is executed after the JavaScript from the <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> field.'=>'JavaScript, der opbevares i feltet <translation-key id="Initialization">Initialisering</translation-key>, udføres hver gang indholdsblokering ophører (dvs. lige så mange gange, som den besøgende fjerner indholdsblokering). Det udføres bagefter JavaScript fra <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key>-feltet.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextFor legal compliance, every <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> must be linked to a specific <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>.'=>'For at overholde lovgivningen skal alle <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokker</translation-key>e være knyttet til en bestemt <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyder</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextIn the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> section (found under <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Consent Management</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Providers">Providers</translation-key>), you will find more information and also have the option to edit or create new <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> entries.'=>'I sektionen <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyder</translation-key> (findes under <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Samtykkehåndtering</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Providers">Udbydere</translation-key>) finder du flere oplysninger og har også mulighed for at redigere eller oprette nye <translation-key id="Provider">Udbyder</translation-key>-poster.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextIt\'s optional, but there are two good reasons why you should link a <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> to a specific <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Det er valgfrit, men der er to gode grunde til, at du bør knytte en <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokker</translation-key> til en bestemt <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextLinking a <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> to a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> enables automatic unblocking of content for visitors upon granting consent to the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> through the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'Ved at linke en <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokker</translation-key> til en <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> kan man automatisk fjerne blokering af indhold for besøgende, når de giver samtykke til <translation-key id="Service">Servicen</translation-key> via <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialogboksen</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextYou can extend the information about the <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>, for example with cookie information, via the linked <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Du kan udvide oplysningerne om <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokkeren</translation-key>, f.eks. med oplysninger om cookies, via den tilknyttede <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextUse the <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> to block content that is not automatically blocked. If contents use the oEmbed format, for example <strong>Pinterest</strong> links, use the <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> to avoid display errors and block the content: {{ shortcode }}'=>'Brug <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcoden</translation-key> til at blokere indhold, der ikke automatisk er blokeret. Hvis indholdet bruger oEmbed-formatet, f.eks. <strong>Pinterest</strong>-links, så brug <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcoden</translation-key> for at undgå visningsfejl og blokere indholdet: {{ shortcode }}','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> is not available until the <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> is created.'=>'<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcoden</translation-key> er ikke tilgængelig, før <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokkeren</translation-key> er oprettet.','Backend / Content Blocker / Label<translation-key id="Execute-Global-code-before-unblocking">Execute Global code before unblocking</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Execute-Global-code-before-unblocking">Udfør global kode før fjerner blokering</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blocker / HintIf this option is enabled and a visitor unblocks the content, the JavaScript in the <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> field will be executed before the blocked content is loaded.'=>'Hvis denne indstilling er aktiveret, og en besøgende fjerner blokeringen af indholdet, vil JavaScript i feltet <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> blive udført, før det blokerede indhold indlæses.','Backend / Content Blocker Language String / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Text-Placeholder">Text Placeholder</translation-key> configured.'=>'Ingen <translation-key id="Text-Placeholder">Tekstpladsholder</translation-key> konfigureret.','Backend / Content Blocker Language String / ButtonAdd Text Placeholder'=>'Tilføj tekstpladsholder','Backend / Content Blocker Host / LabelKey'=>'Nøgle','Backend / Content Blocker Host / LabelText'=>'Tekst','Backend / Content Blocker Language String / Headline<translation-key id="Text-Placeholder">Text Placeholder</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Text-Placeholder">Tekstpladsholder</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blocker Language String / Table Headline<translation-key id="Key">Key</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Key">Nøgle</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blocker Language String / Table Headline<translation-key id="Text">Text</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Text">Tekst</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blocker Language String / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Text-Placeholder">Text Placeholder</translation-key> section?'=>'Hvad er formålet med sektionen <translation-key id="Text-Placeholder">Tekstpladsholder</translation-key>?','Backend / Content Blocker Language String / Things to know / Text<translation-key id="Text-Placeholder">Text Placeholder</translation-key> facilitates the creation of text placeholders for your <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>, streamlining your text adjustment process.'=>'<translation-key id="Text-Placeholder">Tekstpladsholder</translation-key> gør det lettere at oprette tekstpladsholdere til din <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Indholdsblokker</translation-key>, hvilket strømliner din tekstjusteringsproces.','Backend / Content Blocker Language String / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Key">Key</translation-key> you specify can be placed in your <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content">Preview Blocked Content</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-HTML">HTML</translation-key> code using the <strong><em>{{ yourKey }}</em></strong> variable. It will be automatically replaced by the text specified in the <translation-key id="Text">Text</translation-key> field when the content is blocked.'=>'<translation-key id="Key">Nøglen</translation-key>, du angiver, kan placeres i din <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content">Forhåndsvisning af blokeret indhold</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-HTML">HTML</translation-key>-kode ved hjælp af <strong><em>{{ dinNøgle }}</em></strong> variabel. Den vil automatisk blive erstattet af den tekst, der er angivet i feltet <translation-key id="Text">Tekst</translation-key>, når indholdet blokeres.','Backend / Content Blocker Location / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Location">Location</translation-key> configured.'=>'Ingen <translation-key id="Location">Adresse</translation-key> konfigureret.','Backend / Content Blocker Location / ButtonAdd Location'=>'Tilføj adresse','Backend / Content Blocker Location / LabelHostname'=>'Værtsnavn','Backend / Content Blocker Location / LabelPath'=>'Sti','Backend / Content Blocker Location / HeadlineLocations'=>'Adresser','Backend / Content Blocker Location / Table Headline<translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Hostname">Værtsnavn</translation-key>','Backend / API Client / AlertThe scan quota has been exceeded. Please try again later.'=>'Scanningskvoten er overskredet. Prøv igen senere.','Backend / Content Blocker Location / Table Headline<translation-key id="Path">Path</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Path">Sti</translation-key>','Backend / API Client / AlertThe maximum number of pages to scan has been exceeded. Please try again later.'=>'Det maksimale antal sider, der kan scannes, er overskredet. Prøv igen senere.','Backend / Content Blocker Location / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is a <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key>?'=>'Hvad er et <translation-key id="Hostname">Værtsnavn</translation-key>?','Backend / API Client / AlertThe request could not be authorized. Please try again later.'=>'Anmodningen kunne ikke godkendes. Prøv igen senere.','Backend / Content Blocker Location / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Locations">Locations</translation-key> section?'=